%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Who's%20funding%20Hamas%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222672%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20close%20up%20of%20two%20pairs%20of%20hands%20as%20they%20handle%20money%2C%20gold%2C%20and%20bullets.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652f317d96f7540cd05f0034%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222004%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPalestinian%20Hamas%20activists%20receive%20gold%20and%20money%20from%20Palestinians%20during%20a%20donation%20campaign%20to%20support%20Hamas%20and%20the%20Jihad%20following%20prayer%20in%20Gaza%20City%2C%20Gaza%20Strip.%3Cp%3EAbid%20Katib%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3EExperts%20estimate%20that%20Hamas%20has%20an%20operational%20budget%20of%20more%20than%20%24300%20million.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EIt%20gets%20some%20of%20its%20funding%20from%20taxing%20imports%20into%20Gaza%20and%20creating%20misleading%20charities.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EInternational%20ties%20and%20business%20investments%20also%20raise%20money%20for%20the%20Palestinian%20militant%20group.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFighting%20a%20war%20is%20expensive.%20So%20how%20is%20Hamas%20%E2%80%94%20the%20militant%20group%20designated%20a%20terrorist%20organization%20by%20the%20United%20States%20and%20the%20European%20Union%20%E2%80%94%20funding%20their%20battle%20against%20Israel%2C%20which%20receives%20nearly%20%244%20billion%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-aid-spending-israel-military-defense-gaza-war-2023-10%5C%22%3EUS-provided%20military%20aid%3C%2Fa%3E%20per%20year%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20answer%20is%20found%20in%20a%20complex%20web%20of%20business%20investments%2C%20phony%20charities%2C%20crypto%20transactions%2C%20and%20international%20support%20that%20makes%20it%20challenging%20to%20determine%20Hamas'%20exact%20value.%20However%2C%20experts%20estimate%20the%20militant%20organization%20has%20an%20operating%20budget%20of%20hundreds%20of%20millions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHamas%20has%20two%20wings.%20It%20has%20a%20social%20service%20wing%20and%20a%20military%20wing%2C%20and%20the%20social%20service%20wing%20has%20been%20very%20active%20in%20terms%20of%20trying%20to%20raise%20funds%20%E2%80%94%20but%20that%20money%20is%20definitely%20going%20to%20the%20military%2C%26quot%3B%20Victor%20Asal%2C%20director%20of%20the%20Center%20for%20Policy%20Research%20and%20professor%20of%20political%20science%20at%20University%20of%20Albany%2C%20State%20University%20of%20New%20York%2C%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ECounterfeit%20charities%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHistorically%2C%20Hamas-affiliated%20charities%20%E2%80%94%20purported%20to%20provide%20much-needed%20money%20for%20residents%20of%20Gaza%20struggling%20to%20access%20sufficient%20food%20or%20medical%20care%20%E2%80%94%20have%20been%20a%20driver%20of%20funds%20toward%20its%20military%20wing.%20While%20some%20of%20the%20funds%20may%20ultimately%20reach%20their%20intended%20subjects%2C%20often%20the%20charitable%20organizations%2C%20headquartered%20outside%20Gaza%20and%20sometimes%20based%20in%20Western%20countries%2C%20are%20sophisticated%20fronts%20for%20Hamas%20military%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202003%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhome.treasury.gov%2Fnews%2Fpress-releases%2Fjs672%5C%22%3EUS%20Treasury%3C%2Fa%3E%20designated%20five%20different%20charities%20%E2%80%94%20based%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20Switzerland%2C%20Austria%2C%20Lebanon%2C%20and%20France%20%E2%80%94%20as%20terrorist%20organizations%20for%20their%20support%20of%20Hamas.%20In%202009%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.justice.gov%2Fopa%2Fpr%2Ffederal-judge-hands-downs-sentences-holy-land-foundation-case%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJustice%20Department%3C%2Fa%3E%20convicted%20leaders%20from%20the%20US-based%20Holy%20Land%20Foundation%20for%20Relief%20and%20Development%20for%20providing%20financial%20support%20to%20the%20militant%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20international%20crackdown%20on%20Hamas-affiliated%20charities%2C%20the%20group%20has%2C%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20relied%20less%20on%20this%20fundraising%20method.%20However%2C%20it%20remains%20a%20consistent%20source%20of%20income%20for%20the%20militant%20group%2C%20two%20experts%20told%20Insider.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESupport%20from%20Iran%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%20charitable%20fronts%2C%20Matthew%20Levitt%2C%20a%20former%20counterterrorism%20intelligence%20analyst%20at%20the%20Federal%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%2C%20told%20Insider%20that%20international%20support%2C%20mainly%20from%20Iran%2C%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Bthe%20one%20big%20constant%26quot%3B%20in%20Hamas'%20funding%2C%20estimating%20that%20Iran%20contributes%20between%20%2470%20and%20%24100%20million%20a%20year%20to%20support%20the%20militant%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20Iran%20this%20enables%20them%20to%20have%20extended%20reach%20beyond%20their%20borders%2C%20to%20undermine%20adversaries%20%E2%80%94%20and%20they're%20committed%20to%20the%20destruction%20of%20Israel%20%E2%80%94%20it%20also%20enables%20them%2C%20to%20be%20perfectly%20blunt%2C%20to%20fight%20to%20the%20last%20Arab%2C%26quot%3B%20Levitt%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BYou're%20not%20going%20to%20see%20actual%20Iranians%2C%20Persians%2C%20on%20the%20front%20lines%20in%20Lebanon%20or%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%20Iran%20is%20very%20comfortable%20deploying%20Arab%20Muslim%20assets%20who%2C%20when%20they%20do%20something%2C%20will%20be%20the%20ones%20to%20be%20suffering%20the%20brunt%20of%20the%20reprisal%2C%20not%20Iran.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Iran%2C%20Levitt%20said%2C%20funding%20Hamas%20ultimately%20offers%20a%20financially%20and%20politically%20inexpensive%20way%20to%20undermine%20Israel's%20stability%20and%20increase%20the%20pressure%20against%20their%20adversaries%20while%20maintaining%20an%20air%20of%20deniability%20regarding%20its%20involvement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ETaxation%2C%20investments%2C%20and%20smuggling%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20the%20Biden%20administration%20has%20come%20under%20fire%20for%20a%20September%20decision%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fbiden-iran-nuclear-deal-ranian-oil-revenue-frozen-prisoner-swap-2023-9%5C%22%3Erelease%20%246%20billion%20of%20frozen%20Iranian%20oil%20revenue%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0as%20part%20of%20a%20deal%20to%20free%20prisoners%2C%20which%20critics%20argue%20made%20funds%20available%20for%20Iran%20to%20send%20to%20Hamas%20ahead%20of%20the%20attack%20on%20Israel.%20Both%20Asal%20and%20Levitt%20told%20Insider%20the%20funds%20from%20that%20transaction%20had%20little%20to%20do%20with%20the%20latest%20escalation%20in%20the%20conflict%20between%20Hamas%20and%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20while%20Hamas'%20control%20of%20the%20Gaza%20territory%20has%20grown%20with%20financial%20support%20from%20Iran%2C%20so%20has%20the%20group's%20capability%20to%20earn%20money%20from%20the%20land%20it%20controls.%20As%20with%20many%20terrorist%20organizations%20that%20control%20swaths%20of%20land%20or%20trade%20routes%2C%20Hamas%20gets%20funding%20through%20taxation%2C%20extortion%2C%20smuggling%2C%20kidnapping%2C%20and%20robbery%2C%20Asal%20told%20Insider.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELevitt%2C%20who%20currently%20serves%20as%20director%20of%20the%20Reinhard%20program%20on%20counterterrorism%20and%20intelligence%20at%20the%20Washington%20Institute%20for%20Near%20East%20Policy%2C%20said%20Hamas%20oversees%20%26quot%3Banything%20and%20everything%20that%20crosses%20their%20borders%26quot%3B%20and%20controls%20the%20region's%20economic%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20there%20were%20smuggling%20tunnels%20dug%20into%20Egypt%2C%20Hamas%20taxed%20those.%20When%20Qatar%20%E2%80%94%20with%20Israeli%20and%20US%20acquiescence%20%E2%80%94%20was%20giving%20money%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fhamas-unable-pay-salaries-gaza-after-qatari-aid-delay-officials-say-2023-07-16%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DMost%2520of%2520Gaza%2527s%25202.3%2520million%2Chelp%2520pay%2520public%2520sector%2520wages.%5C%22%3Epay%20for%20salaries%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Hamas%20was%20able%20to%20tax%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Levitt%20said.%20%26quot%3BAny%20business.%20Any%20aid%2C%20humanitarian%20aid%2C%20the%20truck%20after%20truck%20after%20truck%20that%20would%20come%20in%20on%20a%20daily%20basis%20from%20Israel%20into%20Gaza%20could%20all%20be%20taxed%20and%20extorted%20%E2%80%94%20so%20the%20largest%20pot%20of%20income%20for%20Hamas%20recently%20has%20not%20been%20Iran%3B%20it's%20been%20controlled%20territory%2C%20and%20the%20ability%20to%20make%20money%20off%20of%20that%3A%20probably%20in%20the%20%24300-400%20or%20%24450%20million%20range.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20funds%20raised%20from%20taxing%20and%20extorting%20residents%20of%20Gaza%2C%20Hamas%20officials%20make%20substantial%20business%20investments%20in%20real%20estate%20and%20construction%20corporations%2C%C2%A0as%20well%20as%20mining%20and%20infrastructure%20companies%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20and%20North%20Africa%20%E2%80%94%20some%20of%20which%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.state.gov%2Ftargeting-covert-hamas-investment-network-and-hamas-finance-official%2F%5C%22%3Edesignated%20terrorist%20organizations%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20State%20Department%20due%20to%20their%20affiliation%20with%20the%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMoney%20laundering%20and%20crypto%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20move%20all%20its%20money%20around%2C%20Levitt%20said%2C%20Hamas%20relies%20largely%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisrael-freezes-hamas-crypto-accounts-binance-helps-2023-10%5C%22%3Ecryptocurrency%20transactions%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20trade-based%20money%20laundering%20to%20avoid%20being%20easily%20tracked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20instead%20of%20sending%20someone%20%24100%2C%20you%20send%20them%20%24100%20worth%20of%20wheat%20or%20sugar%20or%20rice.%20And%20since%20wheat%2C%20sugar%2C%20and%20rice%20need%20to%20go%20into%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20that%20doesn't%20raise%20the%20same%20kind%20of%20eyebrows%2C%26quot%3B%20Levitt%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20if%20you%20send%20it%20to%20Hamas%20there%2C%20which%20is%20easy%20to%20do%20because%20they're%20the%20governing%20entity%2C%20then%20they%20can%20use%20it%20free%20up%20other%20funds.%20They%20can%20use%20it%20to%20give%20to%20their%20constituents%20and%20build%20grassroots%20support%2C%20or%20they%20can%20sell%20it%20and%20use%20that%20money%20as%20they%20as%20they%20see%20fit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20wake%20of%20Israel%20declaring%20war%20on%20Hamas%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fis-biden-giving-humanitarian-aid-to-palestinians-israel-hamas-war-2023-10%5C%22%3EUS%20has%20pledged%20%24100%20million%20in%20humanitarian%20aid%20to%20Palestinians%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fhamas-gaza-humanitarian-aid-diverted-cf356c48%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20may%20ultimately%20end%20up%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20Hamas%20due%20to%20its%20control%20over%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20data-type%3D%5C%22paragraph%5C%22%3ESuch%20aid%20is%20meant%20to%20provide%20drinking%20water%2C%20food%2C%20and%20medical%20care%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20money%20is%20fungible%2C%26quot%3B%20Alex%20Zerden%2C%20a%20former%20senior%20US%20Treasury%20national%20security%20official%2C%20told%20the%20Journal.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20that%20also%20allows%20Hamas%20to%20divert%20money%20from%20providing%20for%20its%20people%20to%20support%20its%20war%20machine.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%