0that%20he%20was%20proud%20to%20see%20%26quot%3Bloyalty%20in%20the%20eyes%20of%20his%20people.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BThey%20(the%20authorities)%20came%20to%20arrest%20her.%20This%20brave%20girl%20faced%20the%20imminent%20threat%2C%26quot%3B%20Nawaz%20Sharif%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20the%20son%20of%20the%20soil.%20My%20daughter%2C%20Maryam%2C%20she%20is%20the%20daughter%20of%20the%20soil%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20proclaimed%20to%20the%20louder%20cheering%20of%20the%20gathering.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ETears%20of%20joy%20and%20love%20between%20a%20daughter%20and%20her%20father.%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FTheEraOfNawazSharif%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23TheEraOfNawazSharif%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F42JH1qQDI6%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F42JH1qQDI6%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%E2%80%94%20PMLN%20DIGITAL%20(%40pmlndigitalpk)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fpmlndigitalpk%2Fstatus%2F1715736536178929905%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2021%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20in%20a%20rare%20public%20display%20of%20affection%20for%20his%20daughter%2C%20Nawaz%20Sharif%20had%20embraced%20his%20weeping%20daughter%20soon%20after%20he%20climbed%20the%20stage%20at%20the%20rally%20grounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMaryam%2C%2049%2C%20is%20PML-N's%20senior%20vice%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENawaz%20Sharif%20came%20almost%20two%20hours%20later%20than%20the%20announced%20time%20of%205%3A30%20pm.%20Till%20that%20time%2C%20Maryam%20held%20the%20fort%20from%20the%20podium%20for%20more%20than%20an%20hour%20as%20the%20restless%20crowds%20joined%20her%20in%20cheering%20their%20leader.%20Wearing%20a%20maroon%20traditional%20salwar%20kameez%20with%20the%20chunni%20never%20leaving%20her%20head%2C%20Maryam%20spoke%20extempore%20like%20a%20seasoned%20politician.