new%20project%20called%20'Udbhav'%20to%20integrate%20ancient%20strategic%20knowledge%20with%20modern%20military%20practices.%20The%20project%20aims%20to%20address%20modern%20security%20challenges%20and%20prepare%20for%20future%20battles.%20It%20draws%20inspiration%20from%20ancient%20treatises%20such%20as%20Arthashastra%2C%20Nitisara%2C%20and%20The%20Kural%2C%20as%20well%20as%20centuries-old%20military%20campaigns.%20While%20some%20have%20questioned%20the%20project's%20relevance%20in%20today's%20digitized%20battlefields%2C%20the%20government%20and%20the%20Army%20are%20enthusiastic%20about%20integrating%20India's%20military%20heritage%20with%20contemporary%20military%20pedagogy.%20The%20project%20aims%20to%20synthesize%20ancient%20wisdom%20with%20modern%20practices%20to%20develop%20a%20unique%20approach%20to%20security%20challenges.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22RAJAT%20PANDIT%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Frajnath-launches-armys-project-udbhav-to-integrate-ancient-strategic-acumen-with-contemporary-military-practices%2Farticleshow%2F104615090.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gaza%20Children%20Traumatised%20By%20Bombardment.%20Israel's%20Ground%20Offensive%20Looms%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EGaza's%20children%20are%20showing%20ever%20more%20signs%20of%20trauma%20two%20weeks%20into%20Israel's%20intense%20bombardment%2C%20parents%20and%20psychiatrists%20in%20the%20tiny%2C%20crowded%20enclave%20say%2C%20with%20no%20safe%20place%20to%20hide%20from%20the%20falling%20bombs%20and%20little%20prospect%20of%20respite.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChildren%20make%20up%20about%20half%20of%20Gaza's%202.3%20million%20population%2C%20living%20under%20near%20constant%20bombardment%20with%20many%20packed%20into%20temporary%20shelters%20in%20UN-run%20schools%20after%20fleeing%20their%20homes%20with%20little%20food%20or%20clean%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael%20is%20expected%20to%20launch%20a%20ground%20attack%20on%20Gaza%20shortly%20in%20response%20to%20a%20cross-border%20assault%20by%20Hamas%20fighters%20on%20southern%20Israel%20on%20October%207%20that%20killed%20more%20than%201%2C400%20people%2C%20with%20a%20further%20210%20taken%20hostage.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChildren%20...%20have%20started%20to%20develop%20serious%20trauma%20symptoms%20such%20as%20convulsions%2C%20bed-wetting%2C%20fear%2C%20aggressive%20behaviour%2C%20nervousness%2C%20and%20not%20leaving%20their%20parents'%20sides%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Gaza%20psychiatrist%20Fadel%20Abu%20Heen.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMore%20than%204%2C100%20Palestinians%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20Gaza%20so%20far%2C%20including%20more%20than%201%2C500%20children%2C%20while%2013%2C000%20people%20have%20been%20injured%20according%20to%20the%20Palestinian%20health%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EConditions%20in%20makeshift%20shelters%20in%20United%20Nations%20schools%2C%20where%20more%20than%20380%2C000%20people%20are%20camped%20out%20in%20hope%20of%20escaping%20the%20bombardment%2C%20only%20compound%20the%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20sometimes%20100%20people%20sleeping%20in%20each%20classroom%2C%20which%20all%20require%20continuous%20cleaning.%20There%20is%20little%20electricity%20and%20water%20so%20bathrooms%20and%20toilets%20are%20very%20dirty.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20children%20suffer%20a%20lot%20at%20night.%20They%20cry%20all%20night%2C%20they%20pee%20themselves%20without%20meaning%20to%20and%20I%20don't%20have%20time%20to%20clean%20up%20after%20them%2C%20one%20after%20the%20other%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Tahreer%20Tabash%2C%20a%20mother%20of%20six%20children%20sheltering%20in%20a%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEven%20there%2C%20they%20are%20not%20safe.%20Such%20schools%20have%20been%20hit%20several%20times%2C%20the%20United%20Nations%20has%20said%2C%20and%20Tabash%20has%20seen%20strikes%20hitting%20nearby%20buildings.%20When%20her%20children%20hear%20so%20much%20as%20a%20chair%20being%20moved%2C%20they%20jump%20in%20fear%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20lack%20of%20any%20safe%20place%20has%20created%20a%20general%20sense%20of%20fear%20and%20horror%20among%20the%20entire%20population%20and%20children%20are%20most%20impacted%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Abu%20Heen.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20of%20them%20reacted%20directly%20and%20expressed%20their%20fears.%20Although%20they%20may%20need%20immediate%20intervention%2C%20they%20may%20be%20in%20a%20better%20state%20than%20the%20other%20kids%20who%20kept%20the%20horror%20and%20trauma%20inside%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMENTAL%20TOLL%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20house%20in%20Khan%20Younis%2C%20in%20the%20south%20of%20the%20enclave%2C%20is%20sheltering%20about%2090%20people%20including%2030%20under%20the%20age%20of%2018%2C%20where%20they%20have%20to%20sleep%20in%20shifts%20for%20lack%20of%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20there's%20an%20explosion%20or%20any%20target%20getting%20hit%20nearby%20they%20are%20always%20screaming%2C%20always%20frightened.%20We%20try%20to%20calm%20the%20younger%20ones%2C%20try%20telling%20them%2C%20'Don't%20worry%2C%20it's%20just%20fireworks'.%20But%20the%20older%20ones%20understand%20what's%20going%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ibrahim%20al-Agha%2C%20an%20engineer%20sheltering%20in%20the%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20will%20need%20a%20lot%20of%20support%20mentally%20after%20this%20war%20finishes%2C%26quot%3B%20Agha%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Gaza's%20healthcare%20system%20was%20already%20over-stretched%20before%20this%20month's%20war%2C%20which%20has%20pushed%20it%20to%20the%20brink%20of%20collapse%2C%20and%20mental%20health%20experts%20have%20long%20warned%20of%20the%20terrible%20toll%20that%20was%20already%20being%20exacted%20on%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%202022%20report%20by%20aid%20group%20Save%20the%20Children%20found%20the%20psychosocial%20wellbeing%20of%20children%20in%20G