e%20basement%20of%20the%20Capitol%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Florida%20Republican%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20as%20swampy%20as%20swamp%20gets%2C%20and%20Jim%20Jordan%20deserved%20better%20than%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20GOP%20conference%20on%20Friday%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhouse-republicans-vote-closed-door-dump-jim-jordan-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evoted%3C%2Fa%3E%20112-86%20to%20ditch%20Jordan%20as%20their%20nominee%20after%20the%20lawmaker%20lost%20his%20third%20vote%20on%20the%20House%20floor%2C%20which%20once%20again%20threw%20open%20the%20contest%20for%20speaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20the%20conference%20is%20set%20to%20reassemble%20to%20hear%20pitches%20from%20the%20multitude%20of%20Republicans%20who%20have%20thrown%20their%20hat%20into%20the%20ring%2C%20from%20higher-profile%20members%20like%20House%20Majority%20Whip%20Tom%20Emmer%20of%20Minnesota%20and%20Rep.%20Byron%20Donalds%20of%20Florida%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjim-jordan-speaker-house-stalled-austin-scott-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elesser-known%20candidates%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20Reps.%20Jack%20Bergman%20of%20Michigan%20and%20Austin%20Scott%20of%20Georgia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20Gaetz%20filed%20a%20motion%20to%20vacate%20the%20chair%2C%20which%20forced%20a%20vote%20on%20McCarthy's%20speakership.%20Gaetz%20for%20weeks%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgaetz-threatens-mccarthy-motion-to-vacate-house-speakership-biden-spending-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eteased%3C%2Fa%3E%20using%20the%20tool%20against%20McCarthy%2C%20frustrated%20at%20what%20he%20said%20was%20the%20Californian's%20insufficient%20support%20of%20deep%20spending%20cuts%20favored%20by%20the%20conference's%20most%20conservative%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20after%20McCarthy%20averted%20a%20government%20shutdown%20by%20passing%20a%20clean%20continuing%20resolution%20that%20passed%20with%20bipartisan%20support%2C%20the%20House%20voted%20216-210%20to%20boot%20him%20from%20the%20position.%20Eight%20Republicans%20joined%20208%20Democrats%20to%20remove%20McCarthy%20from%20the%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20course%20of%20several%20days%2C%20the%20GOP%20conference%20has%20seen%20House%20Majority%20Leader%20Steve%20Scalise%20of%20Louisiana%20enter%20the%20race%20before%20withdrawing%20after%20he%20attracted%20insufficient%20support%20to%20hit%20the%20217-mark%20threshold%20needed%20to%20win%20the%20speakership.%20And%20Jordan%20is%20the%20latest%20candidate%20who's%20been%20unable%20to%20stave%20off%20enough%20GOP%20defections%20in%20the%20221-member%20majority%20to%20secure%20the%20speaker's%20gavel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhoever%20becomes%20the%20next%20speaker%20will%20have%20to%20navigate%20a%20GOP%20caucus%20deeply%20divided%20on%20spending%2C%20approaches%20to%20governance%2C%20and%20personal%20grievances.%20Democrats%20could%20potentially%20be%20in%20the%20mix%20to%20back%20a%20particular%20GOP%20speaker%20nominee%20if%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vox.com%2Fpolitics%2F2023%2F10%2F19%2F23923926%2Fhouse-speaker-jordan-mchenry-coalition-government%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esome%20sort%20of%20legislative%20deals%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20made%2C%20but%20it%20is%20unclear%20what%20those%20terms%20would%20look%20like%20or%20if%20it%20would%20actually%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmatt-gaetz-jim-jordan-house-republicans-secret-ballot-speaker-nominee-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697904088000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6533e98596f7540cd0627050%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmatt-gaetz-jim-jordan-house-republicans-secret-ballot-speaker-nominee-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20House%20Republican%20conference%20voted%20112-86%20to%20ditch%20Jim%20Jordan%20as%20the%20party's%20speaker%20nominee%20after%20Jordan%20lost%20his%20third%20vote%20on%20the%20House%20floor.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(John%20L.%20Dorman)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A78%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmatt-gaetz-jim-jordan-house-republicans-secret-ballot-speaker-nominee-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'How%20Do%20They%20Build%20That'%3F%3A%20Why%20Smriti%20Irani's%20Claims%20on%20Global%20Hunger%20Index%20Don't%20Offer%20the%20Full%20Picture%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F21211940%2FScreenshot-2023-10-21-at-9.16.51.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Speaking%20at%20a%20FICCI%20event%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%20Union%20minister%20Smriti%20Irani%20said%20that%20the%20Global%20Hunger%20Index%20%E2%80%93%20in%20which%20India%20stood%20at%20111th%20out%20of%20125%20countries%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FPTI_News%2Fstatus%2F1715021411683598388%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Ewas%20compiled%20by%20calling%203%2C000%20people%20in%20India%20and%20asking%20if%20they%20were%20hungry.%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Findia-ranks-111th-among-125-countries-in-global-hunger-index-report%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20report%20makers%E2%80%99%20summary%20rejection%20of%20the%20Indian%20government%E2%80%99s%20assertions.%20However%2C%20this%20time%2C%20what%20also%20garnered%20outrage%20was%20Irani%E2%80%99s%20assertion%20that%20she%20had%20had%20a%20trying%20day%20and%20that%20she%20would%20have%20also%20said%20she%20was%20hungry%20had%20she%20been%20called%20on%20the%20phone%20on%20that%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20Congress%20has%20called%20Irani%20out%20for%20her%20%E2%80%9Cinsensitivity%E2%80%9D%20and%20for%20making%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmockery%20of%20hunger%2C%E2%80%9D%20Irani%E2%80%99s%20claim%20that%20the%20Index%20functions%20this%20way%20is%20not%20correct.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20what%20Irani%20said%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20instance%2C%20Global%20Hunger%20Index%20that%20makes%20headlines%20now%2C%20many%20a%20people%20have%20said%20it%E2%80%99s%20all%20hogwash.%20How%20do%20they%20build%20that%20indice%3F%203%2C000%20people%20in%20a%20country%20of%20a%20140%20crore%20get%20a%20phone%20call%20from%20Gallup%20and%20they%20are%20asked%2C%20%E2%80%98Are%20you%20hungry%3F%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWriting%20for%3Cem%3E%20The%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Banjot%20Kaur%20had%20noted%20in%20her%20report%20that%20this%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20the%20Indian%20government%20has%20rejected%20this%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20October%2012%20statement%2C%20the%20government%20had%20questioned%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.globalhungerindex.org%2Fmethodology.html%5C%22%3Ethe%20selection%20of%20the%20four%20parameters%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20among%20which%20is%20the%20opinion%20poll%20Irani%20referred%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKaur%20quoted%20the%20government%20as%20having%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9CThree%20out%20of%20the%20four%20indicators%20used%20for%20calculation%20of%20the%20index%20are%20related%20to%20the%20health%20of%20children%20and%20cannot%20be%20representative%20of%20the%20entire%20population.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThus%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20own%20assertion%20makes%20one%20aspect%20clear%20%E2%80%93%20which%20contradicts%20Irani%E2%80%99s%20claim%20of%20%E2%80%9Chow%20they%20build%20that%E2%80%9D%20index%3A%20it%20depends%20on%20four%20parameters%2C%20not%20the%20single%20one%20on%20the%20opinion%20poll%2C%20as%20she%20indicated%20in%20the%20speech.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERight%20afterwards%2C%20Irani%20said%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CNow%20trust%20me%2C%20I%20have%20left%20my%20house%20in%20Delhi%20in%20the%20morning%20at%204%20today.%20I%20got%20a%20flight%20at%205%20to%20go%20to%20Kochi.%20I%20did%20a%20conclave%20there.%20Got%20a%20flight%20at%205%20o%E2%80%99clock%20to%20come%20to%20this%20programme.%20By%20the%20time%20I%20get%20to%20anything%20called%20food%2C%20it%20will%20be%2010%20o%E2%80%99clock.%20If%20you%20would%20have%20called%20me%20anytime%20during%20the%20day%20today%20and%20asked%20from%20Gallup%2C%20%E2%80%9CAre%20you%20hungry%3F%E2%80%9D%20I%E2%80%99ll%20say%2C%20%E2%80%9COh%20yes%2C%20I%20am.%E2%80%9D%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20call%20that%20Irani%20claims%20she%20would%20have%20been%20compelled%20to%20attend%20while%20hungry%20aims%20to%20fix%20the%20%E2%80%98Proportion%20of%20Undernourished%E2%80%99%20or%20PoU%20population.%20The%20Indian%20government%20has%20claimed%20that%20it%20is%20based%20on%20an%20opinion%20poll%20conducted%20on%20a%20%E2%80%9Cvery%20small%20sample%20size%20of%203000.%E2%80%9D%20The%20government%E2%80%99s%20reservations%20are%20in%20line%20with%20Irani%E2%80%99s%20claim.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20as%20Kaur%20writes%20in%20her%20report%2C%20the%20GHI%20report%20makers%2C%20in%20an%20emailed%20response%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Eon%20October%2013%2C%20had%20said%20that%20the%20PoU%20rate%20is%20just%20one-third%20of%20the%20total%20GHI%20score.%20More%20importantly%20for%20the%20scope%20of%20Irani%E2%80%99s%20assertions%2C%20the%20PoU%20is%20arrived%20from%20the%20study%20of%20several%20underlying%20parameters%20%E2%80%93%20%3Cem%3Eand%20not%20just%20from%20the%20opinion%20poll.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Index%20considered%20food%20balance%20reports%20that%2C%20Kaur%20reports%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20emailed%20responses%2C%C2%A0was%20partly%20arrived%20at%20%3Cem%3Eusing%20data%20sources%20officially%20given%20by%20the%20Indian%20government%20itself.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIrani%20is%20thus%20publicly%20commenting%20against%20her%20own%20government%E2%80%99s%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20since%20India%E2%80%99s%20latest%20relevant%20data%20was%20collected%20in%202011%2C%20the%20distribution%20of%20calorie%20intake%20in%20the%20population%20was%20estimated%20using%20the%20Food%20Insecurity%20Experience%20Scale%20(FIES)%20survey%20data%2C%20for%20which%20the%20Gallup%20World%20Poll%20was%20used%2C%20the%20report%20makers%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThus%2C%20this%20poll%20was%20part%20of%20an%20indicator%20which%20was%20a%20part%20of%20four%20indicators%20which%20ultimately%20contributed%20to%20the%20Index%20score.%20And%20not%20the%20sole%20indicator%2C%20as%20Irani%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20claim%20is%20also%2C%20as%20mentioned%20earlier%2C%20rendered%20false%20by%20the%20Indian%20government%E2%80%99s%20own%20objections%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3Eother%3C%2Fem%3E%20indicators%20%E2%80%93%20indicating%20at%20least%20that%20there%20are%20other%20indicators.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENo%20other%20government%20has%20disputed%20the%20GHI%E2%80%99s%20methodology.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIrani%20also%20says%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnd%20that%20indice%20(%3Cem%3Esic%3C%2Fem%3E)%20says%20Pakistan%20is%20better%20than%20India.%20Can%20you%20imagine%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Index%2C%20Pakistan%20does%20rank%20above%20India.%20At%20102%2C%20it%20is%20nine%20spots%20above%20India.%20But%20in%20many%20categories%2C%20its%20performance%20is%20comparable%20to%20India%E2%80%99s.%20Its%20percentage%20of%20people%20suffering%20from%20child%20stunting%20(37.6%25)%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20is%20similar%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20(35.5%25).%20The%20Index%20reports%20notes%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20floods%20and%20its%20impact%20on%20crops%2C%20which%20directly%20affect%20food%20consumption.%20It%20also%20pays%20attention%20to%20Indian%20farmers%E2%80%99%20particular%20struggles%2C%20without%20attempting%20to%20compare%20the%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20following%20video%20offers%20a%20deeper%20dive%20into%20the%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fqvh82sP4FhM%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Why%20India%20Ranks%20111%20Out%20of%20125%20Countries%20in%20Hunger%3F%20%7C%20Global%20Hunger%20Index%20Report%20%7C%20Indian%20Government%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22473%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697903474000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F21211940%2FScreenshot-2023-10-21-at-9.16.51.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fglobal-hunger-index-smriti-irani-gallup-poll%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20Banjot%20Kaur%20wrote%20in%20her%20report%20for%20The%20Wire%2C%20the%20GHI%20report%20makers%20have%20said%20that%20the%20Proportion%20of%20Undernourished%20rate%20is%20just%20one-third%20of%20the%20total%20GHI%20score.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fglobal-hunger-index-smriti-irani-gallup-poll%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kane%20Williamson's%20Hilarious%20Post%20Featuring%20The%20Great%20Khali%20Goes%20Viral%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENew%20Zealand%20skipper%20Kane%20Williamson%20on%20Friday%20shared%20a%20picture%20with%20former%20WWE%20wrestler%20The%20Great%20Khali%20on%20Instagram%20and%20added%20a%20cheeky%20caption.%20Mr%20Williamson%20is%20currently%20in%20India%20for%20the%202023%20World%20Cup.%20However%2C%20he%20might%20not%20be%20seen%20on%20the%20field%20for%20the%20next%20three%20matches%20because%20of%20his%20fractured%20thumb.%20He%20sustained%20the%20injury%20while%20running%20between%20wickets%20against%20Bangladesh%20on%20Friday.%20Now%20amidst%20his%20recovery%2C%20the%20New%20Zealand%20captain%2