%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F2024-election%2Fvivek-ramaswamy-wants-us-iron-dome-not-simple-rcna121369%5C%22%3Eadded%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CForeign%20policy%20establishment%20has%20spent%20our%20national%20defence%20budget%20on%20basically%20everything%20other%20than%20defending%20the%20homeland.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20Iron%20Dome%20is%20an%20anti-missile%20defence%20system%20used%20by%20Israel.%20It%20is%20designed%20to%20intercept%20and%20destroy%20short-range%20rockets%20and%20artillery%20shells%20fired%20from%20distances%20of%204%20to%2070%20kilometres%20(approximately%202.5%20to%2043%20miles).%20The%20system%20uses%20radar%20to%20detect%20incoming%20projectiles%20and%20then%20launches%20interceptor%20missiles%20to%20destroy%20them%20in%20the%20air%20before%20they%20reach%20their%20intended%20targets%20on%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DyPLi3lBa0mw%5C%22%3EIron%20Dome%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20effective%20in%20protecting%20certain%20Israeli%20cities%20and%20communities%20from%20rocket%20attacks%20by%20Hamas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECan%20the%20US%20have%20an%20Iron%20Dome%20of%20its%20own%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EImplementing%20a%20system%20like%20the%20Iron%20Dome%20in%20the%20United%20States%20poses%20several%20challenges.%20The%20US%20doesn't%20encounter%20the%20same%20threat%20of%20short-range%20missile%20barrages%20from%20neighbouring%20territories%20that%20the%20Iron%20Dome%20is%20designed%20to%20counter.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20has%20already%20invested%20heavily%20in%20resources%2C%20including%20hundreds%20of%20billions%20of%20dollars%20and%20decades%20of%20development%2C%20into%20addressing%20next-generation%20missile%20threats.%20It's%20not%20an%20overlooked%20issue%2C%20as%20Vivek%20Ramaswamy%20suggested%2C%20but%20rather%20a%20complex%20and%20ongoing%20aspect%20of%20US%20defence%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20a%202023%20Congressional%20Research%20Service%20report%20explains%20that%20each%20Iron%20Dome%20battery%20covers%20about%2060%20square%20miles.%20To%20protect%20the%20entire%20US%2C%20thousands%20of%20such%20batteries%20would%20be%20needed%2C%20and%20they%20might%20not%20defend%20against%20the%20advanced%20hypersonic%20missiles%20that%20Mr%20Ramaswamy%20mentioned.%20It%20is%20a%20complex%20and%20massive%20task%20for%20a%20large%20country%20like%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697902980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F6jgbfcqo_vivek-ramaswamy-afp-_625x300_24_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fvivek-ramaswamy-pushes-israel-type-iron-dome-in-badly-vulnerable-us-4502979%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20United%20States%20should%20have%20its%20version%20of%20the%20Israeli%20Iron%20Dome%20missile%20defence%20system%20to%20protect%20against%20foreign%20threats%2C%20Republican%20presidential%20hopeful%20Vivek%20Ramaswamy%20has%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fvivek-ramaswamy-pushes-israel-type-iron-dome-in-badly-vulnerable-us-4502979%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fvivek-ramaswamy-pushes-israel-type-iron-dome-in-badly-vulnerable-us-4502979%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fvivek-ramaswamy-pushes-israel-type-iron-dome-in-badly-vulnerable-us-4502979%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Russia's%20Kinzhal%20ballistic%20missile%20performs%20poorly%2C%20despite%20Putin's%20hype%20they're%20unstoppable%2C%20says%20UK%20intel%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222835%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mikoyan%20MiG-31K%20fighter%20jets%20with%20Kinzhal%20hypersonic%20missiles%20fly%20over%20Moscow's%20Red%20Square%20during