r%2072%20hours.%20This%20schedule%20puts%20his%20body%20in%20a%20state%20where%20he's%20%26quot%3Bvery%2C%20very%20focused%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Insider.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20all%20part%20of%20what%20the%20HubKonnect%20CEO%20calls%20his%20%26quot%3Bcognitive%20protocol%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%93%20a%20rigorous%20set%20of%20diet%2C%20exercise%2C%20work%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsleep-hacks-to-optimize-business-performance-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esleep%20habits%3C%2Fa%3E%20he%20follows%20to%20optimize%20performance%2C%20and%20they're%20detailed%20in%20his%20recent%20book%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D37f44638200678288b5a618942935b9eb2b34d287d04e9dfebfffbc5de164a94%26postID%3D6533cca2cf767c5e2eaf0ae4%26postSlug%3Dai-entrepreneur-fasts-23-hours-day-eats-once-intermittent-fasting-2023-10%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FPerformance-CEO-Cognitive-Protocol-Entrepreneurial%252Fdp%252FB0CH2M9K8N%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Performance%20CEO.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKoch%2C%2045%2C%20is%20most%20enthusiastic%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fdiet-nutrition%2Fintermittent-fasting-benefits%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eintermittent%20fasting%3A%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3BThe%20benefits%20of%20this%20from%20a%20cognitive%20perspective%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20physical%20perspective%2C%20are%20amazing.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20protocol%20is%20not%20about%20health.%20The%20former%20college%20athlete%20said%20he%20was%20used%20to%20eating%20healthily%2C%20and%20working%20out.%20When%20he%20started%20getting%20more%20business%2C%20though%2C%20Koch%20says%20he%20realized%20he%20needed%20to%20change%20his%20habits%20to%20cope%20with%20his%20workload.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20consulted%20with%20medical%20specialists%2C%20biohacke