kely%20increase%20in%20pollution%20levels%2C%20the%20Centre's%20air%20quality%20panel%20on%20Saturday%20directed%20authorities%20in%20the%20National%20Capital%20Region%20to%20increase%20parking%20fees%20to%20discourage%20private%20transport%20and%20enhance%20the%20services%20of%20CNG%20or%20electric%20buses%20and%20metro%20trains.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20action%20comes%20as%20part%20of%20'Stage%20II'%20of%20the%20central%20government's%20pollution%20control%20plan%20known%20as%20the%20'Graded%20Response%20Action%20Plan'%20(GRAP)%2C%20which%20is%20implemented%20in%20the%20Delhi-NCR%20to%20combat%20air%20pollution%20during%20the%20winter%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20meeting%20to%20review%20the%20air%20quality%20situation%20in%20the%20Delhi-NCR%2C%20the%20Commission%20for%20Air%20Quality%20Management%20(CAQM)%2C%20a%20statutory%20body%20responsible%20for%20proactively%20implementing%20GRAP%2C%20said%20forecasts%20by%20the%20India%20Meteorological%20Department%20and%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Tropical%20Meteorology%20suggest%20Delhi's%20overall%20air%20quality%20is%20likely%20to%20dip%20and%20enter%20the%20'very%20poor'%20category%20on%20October%2023%20and%2024%2C%20owing%20to%20unfavourable%20meteorological%20and%20climatic%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDelhi's%2024-hour%20average%20air%20quality%20index%20(AQI)%20stood%20at%20248%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20panel%20therefore%20decided%20to%20invoke%20the%20measures%20under%20Stage%20II%20of%20GRAP%20in%20the%20entire%20NCR%20in%20addition%20to%20steps%20already%20taken%20under%20Stage%20I.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20actions%20as%20envisaged%20under%20Stage-II%20be%20implemented%20in%20right%20earnest%20by%20all%20the%20agencies%20concerned%20in%20NCR%20with%20immediate%20effect%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20all%20Stage-I%20actions%20of%20GRAP%20already%20in%20force%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said%20in%20an%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGRAP%20categorises%20actions%20into%20four%20stages%3A%20Stage%20I%20-%20'Poor'%20(AQI%20201-300)%3B%20Stage%20II%20-%20'Very%20Poor'%20(AQI%20301-400)%3B%20Stage%20III%20-%20'Severe'%20(AQI%20401-450)%3B%20and%20Stage%20IV%20-%20'Severe%20Plus'%20(AQI%20%3E450).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EStage%20I%20mandates%20the%20suspension%20of%20work%20at%20private%20construction%20and%20demolition%20projects%20with%20a%20plot%20size%20equal%20to%20or%20exceeding%20500%20square%20metres%20that%20are%20not%20registered%20on%20the%20state%20government's%20portal%20for%20remote%20monitoring%20of%20dust%20mitigation%20measures.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20are%20also%20tasked%20with%20enforcing%20a%20complete%20ban%20on%20the%20use%20of%20coal%20and%20firewood%20in%20'tandoors'%20at%20hotels%2C%20restaurants%20and%20open%20eateries%2C%20along%20with%20taking%20punitive%20action%20against%20polluting%20industrial%20units%20and%20thermal%20power%20plants%20within%20300%20kilometres%20of%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEnsuring%20the%20proper%20implementation%20of%20guidelines%20for%20dust%20mitigation%20at%20construction%20and%20demolition%20project%20sites%20and%20sound%20environmental%20management%20of%20resulting%20waste%20is%20also%20part%20of%20Stage%20I.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EStage%20II%20measures%20involve%20increasing%20parking%20fees%20to%20discourage%20private%20transport%20and%20enhancing%20CNG%20or%20electric%20bus%20and%20metro%20services%20by%20introducing%20additional%20fleets%20and%20increasing%20service%20frequency.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUnder%20Stage%20III%2C%20BS-III%20petrol%20and%20BS-IV%20diesel%20four-wheelers%20are%20prohibited%20from%20operating%20in%20Delhi%2C%20Gurugram%2C%20Faridabad%2C%20Ghaziabad%2C%20and%20Gautam%20Buddh%20Nagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EStage%20III%20involves%20a%20complete%20halt%20on%20construction%20and%20demolition%20work%2C%20except%20for%20essential%20government%20projects%2C%20besides%20mining%20and%20stone%20crushing.%20It%20also%20includes%20a%20ban%20on%20the%20entry%20of%20light%20commercial%20vehicles%20registered%20outside%20Delhi%20and%20diesel-guzzling%20trucks%2C%20and%20medium%20and%20heavy%20goods%20vehicles%20(except%20those%20involved%20in%20essential%20services).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EStage%20IV%20includes%20banning%20all%20types%20of%20construction%20and%20demolition%20work.%20State%20governments%20are%20authorised%20to%20decide%20on%20online%20classes%20for%20school%20students%20and%20work-from-home%20arrangements%20for%20government%20and%20private%20offices%20during%20such%20situations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697896920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-12%2Fquj1vgd_delhi-pollution-pti-delhi-air-quality-pti-photo_625x300_16_December_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-air-quality-worsens-stage-2-of-centres-anti-pollution-plan-invoked-4502894%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20a%20likely%20increase%20in%20pollution%20levels%2C%20the%20Centre's%20air%20quality%20panel%20directed%20authorities%20in%20the%20National%20Capital%20Region%20to%20increase%20parking%20fees%20to%20discourage%20private%20transport%20and%20enhance%20the%20services%20of%20CNG%20or%20electric%20buses%20and%20metros.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-air-quality-worsens-stage-2-of-centres-anti-pollution-plan-invoked-4502894%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-air-quality-worsens-stage-2-of-centres-anti-pollution-plan-invoked-4502894%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-air-quality-worsens-stage-2-of-centres-anti-pollution-plan-invoked-4502894%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Antony%20Blinken%20has%20worked%20