0moving%20narcotics%20via%20unmanned%20aerial%20systems%20(UASs%20or%20drones)%20are%20plenteous.%20The%20method%20had%20also%20caught%20on%20along%20the%20India-Pakistan%20international%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fin-combating-drug-trafficking-knowing-the-enemy-is-the-first-step%5C%22%3EIn%20Combating%20Drug%20Trafficking%2C%20Knowing%20the%20Enemy%20Is%20the%20First%20Step%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20lately%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20distinct%20escalation%20of%20drone-assisted%20cross-border%20delivery%20of%20drugs%20and%20weapons%20along%20the%20northern%20border%20areas.%20Since%202020%2C%20such%20drone%20deliveries%20have%20increased%20fourfold.%20On%20October%2012%2C%20the%20Border%20Security%20Force%20(BSF)%2C%20in%20a%20joint%20search%20operation%20with%20the%20police%2C%20captured%20a%20drone%20carrying%203.213%20kg%20payload%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20Daliri%20Village%20in%20Tarn%20Taran%20District.%20Drone%20intrusions%20occur%20almost%20every%20day%20in%20border%20areas%20of%20Punjab%20%E2%80%95%20Fazilka%2C%20Ferozepur%2C%20Tarn%20Taran%2C%20Amritsar%2C%20and%20Gurdaspur.%20This%20month%2C%20until%20October%2014%2C%20there%20were%20four%20separate%20drone%20sightings.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20drone%20operations%20are%20orchestrated%20by%20Pakistan-based%20associates%2C%20and%20the%20drones%20are%20of%20Chinese%20origin%2C%20most%20commonly%20the%20DJI%20Matrice%20300%20RTK%2C%20DJI%20Matrix%20350%20RTK%20or%20DJI%20Mavic%203%20classic%20variants.%20The%20Matrix%20is%20a%20%E2%80%98next-generation%20drone%E2%80%99%20with%20a%20live%20video%20transmission%20system%20visible%20from%20as%20far%20as%2020%20km%2C%20an%20%E2%80%98efficient%20battery%E2%80%99%20for%2055%20minutes%20of%20flying%20time%20and%20%E2%80%98robust%E2%80%99%20compatibility%20to%20carry%20four%20payloads%20at%20once%2C%20with%2010%20kg%20of%20additional%20payload%20capacity.%20The%20batteries%20are%20rechargeable%20up%20to%20400%20cycles.%20The%20flight%20data%20of%20captured%20drones%20reveals%20that%20they%20had%20not%20only%20been%20operational%20within%20Pakistan%20but%20had%20also%20flown%20in%20China.%20The%20embedded%20chip%20in%20the%20drones%20contained%20coordinates%20that%20pointed%20to%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F86220104-97df-48d4-ad9f-f6548cd78dc7%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiMzkzd3kifQ.79ToIT4g5F7ucMIImLdF7NU-uf5OIjhSLr6XIbot9Uc%5C%22%3Eairborne%20presence%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Chinese%20territory%20and%20subsequently%20in%20Khanewal%2C%20in%20Punjab%20province%20of%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2FIndo-Pak-border-copy.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-135478%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221153%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERepresentational%20image.%20A%20fence%20marking%20a%20part%20of%20the%20India-Pakistan%20border%2C%20which%20is%20going%20from%20porous%20to%20impermeable%20rapidly.%20Credit%3A%20Abhishek%20Baxi%2FFlickr%2C%20CC%20BY-NC%202.0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20utilisation%20of%20high-calibre%20drones%20in%20the%20cross-border%20delivery%20of%20weapons%20and%20narcotics%20for%20anti-India%20activities%20is%20beyond%20the%20capacity%20of%20criminal%20gangs%2C%20and%20is%20happening%20with%20active%20state%20sponsorship.%20The%20influx%20of%20narcotics%20and%20the%20cash%20from%20their%20sale%2C%20along%20with%20weapon%20deliveries%2C%20has%20resulted%20in%20a%20virulent%20hybridisation%20of%20the%20illicit%20drug%20trade%2C%20weapons%20trafficking%2C%20terrorism%20and%20assassinations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20local%20Congress%20leader%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fcongress-leader-shot-dead-in-punjab-baljinder-singh-balli-khalistani-terrorist-arsh-dalla-2437449-2023-09-18%5C%22%3EBaljinder%20Singh%20Balli%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20shot%20at%20his%20house%20in%20Dala%20Village%20in%20Moga%20District%2C%20for%20which%20Canada-based%20gangster-turned-terrorist%20Arshdeep%20Singh%20Gill%20(alias%20Arsh%20Dala)%20claimed%20responsibility%20via%20Facebook.%20In%202020%2C%20Shaurya%20Chakra%20awardee%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tribuneindia.com%2Fnews%2Fpunjab%2Fbalwinders-killing-an-attempt-to-create-terror-claims-ssp-421467%5C%22%3EBalwinder%20Singh%20Sandhu%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20gunned%20down%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20Pakistan-based%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20Lakhbir%20Singh%20Rode.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGangster%20and%20terrorist%20Lakhbir%20Singh%20%E2%80%98Landa%E2%80%99%20faces%20charges%20of%20smuggling%20drugs%2C%20arms%20and%20explosives%20from%20across%20the%20border%2C%20using%20drones.%20Wanted%20for%20several%20targeted%20killings%20in%20Punjab%2C%20Landa%20and%20his%20Czech%20Republic-based%20associate%20Gurdev%20Singh%20Jaisel%2C%20organised%20RPG%20attacks%20at%20the%20Sarhali%20Kalan%20police%20station%20and%20the%20Punjab%20Police%E2%80%99s%20intelligence%20headquarters%20in%20Mohali%20on%20May%209.%20Landa%20received%20consignments%20of%20firearms%2C%20IEDs%20and%20AK47%20rifles%20from%20across%20the%20border.%20In%20the%20past%20year%2C%20Sarhali%20Police%20Station%20in%20Punjab%E2%80%99s%20Tarn%20Taran%20has%20been%20attacked%20more%20than%20half%20a%20dozen%20times%2C%20and%20other%20police%20and%20Army%20establishments%20have%20been%20struck.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAside%20from%20strengthening%20Village%20Defence%20Committees%20(VDCs)%20and%20rewarding%20those%20who%20have%20helped%20curb%20narcotics%20smuggling%2C%20the%20Punjab%20Police%20plan%20to%20use%20Artificial%20Intelligence%20to%20counter%20drone%20and%20narcotics%20threats%20in%20border%20areas.%20Drone%20Emergency%20Response%20System%20(DERS)%20has%20been%20launched%20in%20sections%20of%20the%20border%2C%20but%20it%20is%20not%20foolproof%20and%20more%20comprehensive%2C%20proactive%20and%20collaborative%20countermeasures%20are%20required.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20conventionally%20understood%20that%20drug%20trafficking%20organisations%20and%20terrorist%20groups%20are%20linked%2C%20but%20contemporarily%2C%20this%20linkage%20has%20found%20new%20ground%20in%20India%20through%20backing%20from%20Pakistan.%20With%20increasing%20cases%20of%20%E2%80%98gangsters%E2%80%99%20targeting%20police%20stations%20and%20undertaking%20political%20assassinations%2C%20the%20lines%20distinguishing%20gangsters%20and%20terrorists%20have%20blurred.%20The%20massive%20narcotics%20push%20into%20India%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20being%20a%20challenge%20to%20the%20solvency%20of%20the%20state%2C%20has%20begun%20to%20affect%20the%20moral%20fabric%20of%20society%20by%20creating%20a%20drug%20addiction%20epidemic%20in%20border%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EVaishali%20Basu%20Sharma%20is%20a%20strategic%20and%20economic%20affairs%20analyst.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697896166000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F07%2F15685514648_7f2f76b05c_b.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fdrones-give-new-dimensions-to-narcoterrorism-at-the-india-pakistan-border%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20influx%20of%20narcotics%20and%20the%20cash%20from%20their%20sale%2C%20along%20with%20weapon%20deliveries%2C%20has%20resulted%20in%20a%20virulent%20hybridisation%20of%20the%20illicit%20drug%20trade%2C%20weapons%20trafficking%2C%20terrorism%20and%20assassinations.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fdrones-give-new-dimensions-to-narcoterrorism-at-the-india-pakistan-border%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20Israeli%20Soldier%20Sings%20National%20Anthem%20In%20House%20Destroyed%20By%20Hamas%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmid%20th