%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Two%20faculty%20members%20of%20an%20engineering%20college%20from%20Ghaziabad%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20have%20been%20suspended%20for%20asking%20a%20student%20to%20step%20down%20from%20the%20stage%20after%20he%20greeted%20the%20audience%20during%20a%20student%20induction%20ceremony%20with%20a%20loud%20%E2%80%98Jai%20Shri%20Ram%E2%80%99%20slogan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20the%20religious%20slogan%20has%20gained%20political%20connotations%20with%20the%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20and%20other%20Hindutva%20outfits%20raising%20it%20at%20their%20events%20and%20rallies.%20On%20various%20occasions%20in%20the%20college%20and%20university%20premises%2C%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20student%20wing%2C%20Akhil%20Bharatiya%20Vidyarthi%20Parishad%20(ABVP)%2C%20has%20raised%20such%20slogans%20for%20political%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20video%20clip%20showing%20a%20teacher%20asking%20the%20student%20to%20step%20down%20from%20the%20stage%20on%20October%2020%20was%20circulated%20widely%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%20prompting%20various%20Hindutva%20outfits%20to%20express%20outrage%20at%20the%20teachers%E2%80%99%20action.%20Soon%2C%20another%20video%20clip%2C%20featuring%20a%20different%20faculty%20member%20warning%20students%20that%20no%20programme%20would%20be%20allowed%20if%20they%20chant%20Jai%20Shri%20Ram%20also%20went%20viral.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20outrage%20shown%20by%20Hindutva%20outfits%20soon%20reached%20the%20campus%20with%20Hindu%20Raksha%20Dal%20planning%20a%20protest%20against%20the%20teachers%20%E2%80%93%20Mamta%20Gautam%20and%20Shweta%20Sharma.%20As%20per%20news%20reports%2C%20police%20personnel%20were%20deployed%20at%20the%20campus%20due%20to%20the%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELater%20in%20the%20day%2C%20Sanjay%20Kumar%2C%20the%20director%20of%20ABES%20Engineering%20College%20in%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20Ghaziabad%20district%2C%20took%20to%20social%20media%20to%20state%