ety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Fglobal%2Fklubb-super-8-lumiere-festival-mifc-1235763856%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Fglobal%2Fklubb-super-8-lumiere-festival-mifc-1235763856%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Meryl%20Streep%20And%20Her%20Husband%20Have%20Been%20Separated%20For%20Over%206%20Years%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMeryl%20Street%20and%20her%20husband%20of%2045%20years%2C%20Don%20Gummer%2C%20have%20been%20secretly%20separated%20for%20over%20six%20years%2C%20%3Cem%3EPage%20Six%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20on%20Friday.%20Speaking%20to%20the%20outlet%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20of%20the%20Oscar-winning%20star%20confirmed%20the%20news%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BDon%20Gummer%20and%20Meryl%20Streep%20have%20been%20separated%20for%20more%20than%206%20years%2C%20and%20while%20they%20will%20always%20care%20for%20each%20other%2C%20they%20have%20chosen%20lives%20apart%26quot%3B.%20Notably%2C%20Ms%20Streep%20and%20her%20husband%20tied%20the%20knot%20in%201978%2C%20and%20they%20share%20four%20children%20together%3A%20Henry%2C%2043%2C%20Mamie%2C%2040%2C%20Grace%2037%2C%20and%20Louisa%2C%2032.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpagesix.com%2F2023%2F10%2F20%2Fmeryl-streep-husband-don-gummer-have-been-separated-for-more-than-6-years%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EPage%20Six%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20couple%20was%20last%20seen%20publicly%20together%20at%20the%202018%20Academy%20Awards.%20The%20actor%20was%20nominated%20that%20year%20in%20the%20Best%20Actress%20category%20for%20Steven%20Spielberg's%20%3Cem%3E'The%20Post'%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20couple's%20love%20story%20traces%20back%20to%20decades.%20They%20were%20first%20introduced%20by%20her%20brother%2C%20Harry%2C%20in%201978.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20Ms%20Streep%20had%20been%20mourning%20the%20loss%20of%20her%20late%20boyfriend%20John%20Cazale%2C%20who%20had%20passed%20away%20from%20lung%20cancer%20that%20year.%20Ms%20Streep%20and%20Mr%20Gummer%20wed%20that%20same%20year%20and%20have%20since%20kept%20their%20relationship%20out%20of%20the%20public%20eye.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20her%20marriage%20in%20a%202002%20interview%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vogue.com%2Fslideshow%2Fmeryl-streep-don-gummer-tribute%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EVogue%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Ms%20Streep%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BGoodwill%20and%20willingness%20to%20bend%20-%20and%20to%20shut%20up%20every%20once%20in%20a%20while.%20There's%20no%20road%20map%20on%20how%20to%20raise%20a%20family%3A%20It's%20always%20an%20enormous%20negotiation.%20But%20I%20have%20a%20holistic%20need%20to%20work%20and%20to%20have%20huge%20ties%20of%20love%20in%20my%20life.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20the%20couple%20has%20attended%20countless%20red%20carpet-events%20together.%20At%20the%20Academy%20Awards%20in%202012%2C%20when%20the%20actor%20won%20Best%20Actress%20for%20%3Cem%3E'The%20Iron%20Lady'%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20she%20said%20in%20her%20speech%2C%20%26quot%3BFirst%2C%20I'm%20going%20to%20thank%20Don%20because%20when%20you%20thank%20your%20husband%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20speech%20they%20play%20him%20out%20with%20the%20music%2C%20and%20I%20want%20him%20to%20know%20that%20everything%20I%20value%20most%20in%20our%20lives%2C%20you've%20given%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fx-user-claims-dukaan-has-god-complex-ceo-hits-back-with-sarcastic-reply-4497478%5C%22%3EX%20User%20Claims%20Dukaan%20Has%20''God%20Complex''%2C%20CEO%20Hits%20Back%20With%20Sarcastic%20Reply%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20pair%2C%20who%20both%20attended%20Yale%20University%2C%20also%20saw%20their%20daughter%20enter%20the%20world%20of%20Hollywood.%20Their%20son%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20pursued%20music%20under%20the%20stage%20name%20Henry%20Wolfe.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20have%20five%20grandchildren%20together%20as%20well.%20Their%20son%20has%20two%20children%20with%20his%20wife%20Tomaryn%20Storm%20Hawker.%20Their%20daughter%2C%20Mamie%20Gummer%2C%20has%20two%20children%20with%20her%20husband%20Mehar%20Sethi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20on%20the%20work%20front%2C%20Meryl%20Streep%20was%20last%20seen%20in%20season%20three%20of%20%3Cem%3E'Only%20Murders%20In%20The%20Building'.%3C%2Fem%3E%20According%20to%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnbcmiami.com%2Fentertainment%2Fentertainment-news%2Fmeryl-streep-and-husband-don-gummer-announce-split-after-45-years-of-marriage%2F3139068%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%20NBC%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20she%20holds%20the%20record%20for%20most%20Oscar%20nominations%20of%20any%20actor%20with%2021%2C%20including%20for%20her%20roles%20in%3Cem%3E%20'The%20Post%2C%20'Into%20the%20Woods'%2C%20'The%20Iron%20Lady'%2C%20'The%20Devil%20Wears%20Prada'%2C%20'Out%20of%20Africa'%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3E'Kramer%20vs%20Kramer'.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697889840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fov5v6pp8_meryl-streep_625x300_21_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fmeryl-streep-husband-don-gummer-have-been-separated-for-over-6-years-report-4502785%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Meryl%20Street%20and%20her%20husband%20of%2045%20years%2C%20Don%20Gummer%2C%20have%20been%20secretly%20separated%20for%20over%20six%20years%2C%20Page%20Six%20reported%20on%20Friday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fmeryl-streep-husband-don-gummer-have-been-separated-for-over-6-years-report-4502785%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fmeryl-streep-husband-don-gummer-have-been-separated-for-over-6-years-report-4502785%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fmeryl-streep-husband-don-gummer-have-been-separated-for-over-6-years-report-4502785%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Manual%20Scavenging%3A%20SC%20Hikes%20Compensation%20to%20Rs%2030%20Lakh%2C%20Orders%20Govt%20to%20Ensure%20Complete%20Ban%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F08%2F06191314%2FScreen-Shot-2021-08-06-at-7.12.59-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWhile%20directing%20the%20Union%20and%20state%20governments%20to%20ensure%20the%20complete%20eradication%20of%20manual%20scavenging%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Friday%2C%20October%2020%2C%20ordered%20the%20compensation%20in%20the%20cases%20of%20sewer%20deaths%20to%20be%20increased%20to%20Rs%2030%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20said%20compensation%20amount%20in%20the%20case%20of%20permanent%20disability%20be%20made%20Rs%2020%20lakh%2C%20and%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20be%20given%20for%20other%20forms%20of%20disability.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20division%20Bench%20of%20Justice%20S.%20Ravindra%20Bhat%20and%20Justice%20Aravind%20Kumar%20issued%2014%20directions%20for%20the%20effective%20implementation%20of%20Prohibition%20of%20Employment%20as%20Manual%20Scavengers%20and%20their%20Rehabilitation%20Act%2C%202013.%20The%20orders%20also%20called%20for%20proper%20rehabilitation%20measures%20for%20victims%20and%20their%20families%2C%20including%20the%20disbursement%20of%20scholarships%20and%20the%20availability%20of%20skill%20development%20programmes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Fsupreme-court%2Fcompletely-eradicate-manual-scavenging-supreme-court-directs-union-states-increases-compensation-for-sewer-deaths-to-rs-30-lakh-240650%3Finfinitescroll%3D1%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3ELivelaw%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20court%2C%20passing%20its%20verdict%20in%20a%20public%20interest%20litigation%20against%20the%20employment%20of%20manual%20scavengers%2C%20said%2C%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9CUnion%20and%20States%20are%20duty-bound%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20practice%20of%20manual%20scavenging%20is%20completely%20eradicated.%20Each%20of%20us%20owes%20to%20this%20large%20segment%20of%20the%20population%20who%20have%20remained%20unseen%2C%20unheard%2C%20and%20muted%2C%20in%20bondage%20systematically%20trapped%20in%20inhuman%20conditions.%20The%20conferment%20of%20entitlements%20and%20placement%20of%20obligations%20upon%20the%20Union%20and%20States%20through%20the%20express%20prohibitions%20in%20the%20constitution%20and%20provisions%20of%20the%202013%20Act%20means%20that%20they%20are%20obliged%20to%20implement%20the%20provisions%20in%20the%20letter%20and%20spirit.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20went%20on%20to%20add%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20without%20reason%20that%20our%20constitution%20has%20placed%20great%20emphasis%20on%20the%20value%20of%20dignity%20and%20fraternity.%20But%20for%20these%20two%2C%20all%20other%20liberties%20are%20a%20chimera.%20All%20of%20us%20today%20who%20proudly%20bask%20in%20the%20achievements%20of%20our%20republic%20have%20to%20awake%20and%20arise%20so%20that%20the%20darkness%20which%20has%20been%20the%20fate%20of%20generations%20of%20our%20people%20is%20dispelled%20and%20they%20enjoy%20these%20freedoms%20and%20justice-%20social%2C%20economic%2C%20and%20political%20%E2%80%93%20that%20we%20take%20for%20granted.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20matter%20will%20be%20next%20heard%20on%20February%201%2C%202024%2C%20to%20take%20stock%20of%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20directives.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2F339-lives-lost-to-manual-scavenging-in-the-last-five-years-govt-data-reveals%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Union%20social%20justice%20and%20empowerment%20ministry%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20339%20people%20lost%20their%20lives%20while%20cleaning%20sewers%20and%20septic%20tanks%20in%20India%20between%202018%20and%202023.%20As%20per%20the%20data%20presented%20before%20the%20parliament%20by%20the%20government%2C%C2%A0nine%20such%20deaths%20were%20recorded%20in%202023%2C%2066%20in%202022%2C%2058%20in%202021%2C%2022%20in%202020%2C%20117%20in%202019%2C%20and%2067%20deaths%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EManual%20scavenging%20is%20an%20outlawed%20practice%20under%20the%20Prohibition%20of%20Employment%20as%20Manual%20Scavengers%20and%20their%20Rehabilitation%20(PEMSR)%20Act%2C%202013.%20The%20Act%20bans%20the%20use%20of%20any%20individual%20for%20manually%20cleaning%2C%20carrying%2C%20disposing%20of%2C%20or%20otherwise%20handling%2C%20in%20any%20manner%2C%20human%20excreta%20till%20its%20disposal.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697889625000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F08%2F06191314%2FScreen-Shot-2021-08-06-at-7.12.59-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fmanual-scavenging-sc-hikes-compensation-to-rs-30-lakh-orders-govt-to-ensure-complete-ban%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20division%20Bench%20of%20Justice%20S.%20Ravindra%20Bhat%20and%20Justice%20Aravind%20Kumar%20issued%2014%20directions%20for%20the%20effective%20implementation%20of%20Prohibition%20of%20Employment%20as%20Manual%20Scavengers%20and%20their%20Rehabilitation%20Act%2C%202013.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fmanual-scavenging-sc-hikes-compensation-to-rs-30-lakh-orders-govt-to-ensure-complete-ban%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Workers%20Are%20Striking%20In%20Numbers%20Not%20Seen%20In%20Years%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22But%20any%20talk%20of%20a%20strike%20resurgence%20needs%20to%20be%20put%20in%20the%20historical%20context%20of%20a%20major%20long-term%20decline.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697889602000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fimg.huffingtonpost.com%2Fasset%2F6532fdb2230000fc0954ab7e.jpeg%3Fops%3D1200_630%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Fstrike-workers-labor-statistics-data_n_6532f78de4b011a9cf799ac8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22But%20any%20talk%20of%20a%20strike%20resurgence%20needs%20to%20be%20put%20in%20the%20historical%20context%20of%20a%20major%20long-term%20decline.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A45%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Fstrike-workers-labor-statistics-data_n_6532f78de4b011a9cf799ac8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-huffpost-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Fstrike-workers-labor-statistics-data_n_6532f78de4b011a9cf799ac8%2Famp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Fstrike-workers-labor-statistics-data_n_6532f78de4b011a9cf799ac8%2Famp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BMahua%20Moitra%20Mortgaged%20Country's%20Security%20For%20Money%26quot%3B%3A%20BJP%20MP%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Mahua%20Moitra-Darshan%20Hiranandani%20affidavit%20controversy%20escalated%20on%20Saturday%20with%20both%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20MP%20firing%20salvos%20at%20each%20other.%20While%20MP%20Nishikant%20Dubey%20of%20the%20BJP%20alleged%20the%20TMC%20MP%20had%20mortgaged%20the%20country's%20security%20for%20money%2C%20claiming%20that%20her%20parliamentary%20ID%20was%20used%20in%20Dubai%20when%20she%20was%20in%20India%2C%20Ms%20Moitra%20hit%20back%20and%20accused%20the%20MP%20of%20leaking%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Dubey%2C%20who%20had%20filed%20the%20complaint%20against%20Ms%20Moitra%20before%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%2C%20accusing%20her%20of%20taking%20bribes%20for%20asking%20questions%20in%20Parliament%2C%20alleged%20on%20Saturday%20that%20the%20National%20Informatics%20Centre%20(NIC)%20has%20informed%20an%20investigating%20agency%20that%20her%20ID%20was%20used%20in%20Dubai%20when%20she%20was%20in%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter%2C%20in%20Hindi%2C%20Mr%20Dubey%20wrote%20in%20Hindi%2C%20%26quot%3BAn%20MP%20mortgaged%20the%20country's%20security%20for%20some%20money.%20The%20parliament%20ID%20was%20opened%20in%20Dubai%20when%20the%20so-called%20MP%20was%20in%20India.%20The%20entire%20Indian%20government%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20the%20country%2C%20the%20finance%20department%2C%20the%20central%20agencies%20are%20on%20this%20NIC.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDo%20%40AITCofficial%20and%20the%20opposition%20still%20want%20to%20do%20politics%3F%20It%20is%20the%20public's%20decision.%20NIC%20has%20given%20this%20information%20to%20the%20investigating%20agency%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20without%20taking%20Ms%20Moitra's%20name%20or%20disclosing%20which%20agency%20the%20information%20had%20been%20given%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECountering%20Mr%20Dubey's%20claims%2C%20the%20TMC%20MP%20asked%20the%20NIC%20to%20release%20details%20publicly%20and%20show%20that%20MPs%20were%20physically%20present%20in%20places%20from%20where%20their%20IDs%20were%20accessed%20by%20their%20personal%20assistants%2C%20researchers%2C%20interns%20and%20staff%20members.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20affidavit%2C%20businessman%20Darshan%20Hiranandani%20had%20claimed%20that%20Ms%20Moitra%20had%20given%20him%20her%20parliament%20login%20ID%20to%20frame%20questions%20on%20the%20Adani%20group%2C%20which%20she%20felt%20was%20the%20%26quot%3Bonly%20way%26quot%3B%20to%20target%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20businessman%20claimed%20Ms%20Moitra%20wanted%20to%20quickly%20make%20a%20name%20for%20herself%20at%20the%20national%20level%20and%20she%20was%20told%20by%20her%20friends%20and%20advisors%20that%20the%20shortest%20possible%20route%20to%20fame%20was%20by%20personally%20attacking%20PM%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20TMC%20MP%20made%20frequent%20demands%20and%20kept%20asking%20him%20for%20various%20favours.%20This%20included%20gifting%20her%20expensive%20luxury%20items%2C%20providing%20support%20on%20the%20renovation%20of%20her%20officially%20allotted%20bungalow%20in%20Delhi%2C%20travel%20expenses%20and%20holidays.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMs%20Moitra%20has%20denied%20the%20allegations%20and%20said%20she%20is%20ready%20to%20face%20questions%20from%20the%20Lok%20Sabha's%20Ethics%20Committee%2C%20which%20is%20looking%20into%20Mr%20Dubey's%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Disclaimer%3A%20New%20Delhi%20Television%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20AMG%20Media%20Networks%20Limited%2C%20an%20Adani%20Group%20Company.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697889000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fddm2s7ag_mahua-moitra_625x300_16_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmahua-moitra-mortgaged-countrys-security-for-money-bjp-mp-4502719%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Mahua%20Moitra-Darshan%20Hiranandani%20affidavit%20controversy%20escalated%20on%20Saturday%20with%20both%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20MP%20firing%20salvos%20at%20each%20other.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmahua-moitra-mortgaged-countrys-security-for-money-bjp-mp-4502719%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmahua-moitra-mortgaged-countrys-security-for-money-bjp-mp-4502719%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmahua-moitra-mortgaged-countrys-security-for-money-bjp-mp-4502719%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kajol%20trips%20at%20Durga%20Puja%20pandal%3B%20son%20rescues%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697888929000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104609599%2Cimgsize-37470.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fkajol-trips-at-durga-puja-pandal-son-yug-devgn-comes-to-her-rescue%2Farticleshow%2F104609504.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3