0in%20August.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20payroll%20data%20released%20by%20EPFO%20on%20Friday%2C%20October%2020%2C%20also%20revealed%20that%20the%20share%20of%20women%20also%20decreased%20from%2026.7%25%20(2%2C85%2C%20424)%20in%20July%20to%2026.3%25%20(2%2C43%2C510).%20However%2C%20the%20share%20of%20young%20subscribers%2C%20in%20the%20age%20group%20of%2018-28%2C%20shot%20up%20marginally%20from%2067.97%25%20(7%2C26%2C415)%20in%20July%20to%2068.3%25%20(6%2C32%2C331)%20in%20August%2C%20%3Cem%3EBusiness%20Standard%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Ffresh-formal-job-creation-slows-to-5-month-low-in-august-shows-epfo-data-123102001151_1.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20EPFO%20payroll%20data%20helps%20to%20track%20employment%20creation%20in%20the%20formal%20sector%2C%20as%20it%20is%20mandatory%20for%20every%20new%20employee%20to%20sign%20up%20for%20provident%20fund%20under%20the%20EPFO.%20The%20National%20Statistical%20Office%20(NSO)%20also%20uses%20EPFO%20data%20to%20analyse%20employment%20trends%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20net%20payroll%20addition%20also%20went%20up%20marginally%20by%200.8%25%20to%201.69%20million%20in%20August%20from%20July%201.68%20million.%20The%20net%20payroll%20is%20calculated%20by%20considering%20the%20number%20of%20new%20subscribers%2C%20the%20number%20of%20exits%2C%20and%20the%20return%20of%20old%20subscribers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20should%20be%20noted%20that%20net%20monthly%20payroll%20numbers%20are%20provisional%20in%20nature%20and%20are%20revised%20sharply%20the%20following%20month.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20number%20of%20new%20EPF%20subscribers%20holds%20more%20significance%20than%20net%20additions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERituparna%20Chakraborty%20of%20TeamLease%20Services%20said%20the%20momentum%20found%20in%20the%20labour%20market%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20financial%20year%2C%20which%20generally%20prepares%20a%20holistic%20view%20of%20their%20workforce%20requirement%2C%20lost%20momentum%20by%20monsoon%20time%20as%20more%20people%20took%20to%20work%20in%20the%20agriculture%20sector%2C%20Business%20Standard%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChakraborty%20continued%20to%20add%20that%20with%20the%20onset%20of%20the%20festive%20season%2C%20the%20momentum%20could%20be%20picked%20up%20due%20to%20expected%20demand%20in%20retail%20and%20consumption%20sectors%2C%20resulting%20in%20the%20creation%20of%20new%20formal%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Centre%20for%20Monitoring%20Indian%20Economy%20(CMIE)%2C%20the%20unemployment%20in%20the%20country%20in%20August%20rose%20to%208.1%25%20from%207.9%25%20in%20July%20coupled%20with%20a%20situation%20where%20there%20had%20been%20increased%20labour%20force%20participation%20and%20the%20economy%20was%20not%20able%20to%20create%20jobs%20proportionately.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697887859000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2F28134446%2F3891925784_eb02c9d8e3_o.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fepfo-data-with-13-3-dip-in-new-monthly-subscribers-formal-job-creation-slowed-in-august%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20new%20monthly%20subscribers%20decreased%20from%201.06%20million%20in%20July%20to%209%2C25%2C%20984%20in%20August.%20The%20EPFO%20payroll%20data%20helps%20to%20track%20employment%20creation%20in%20the%20formal%20sector%2C%20as%20it%20is%20mandatory%20for%20every%20new%20employee%20to%20sign%20up%20for%20provident%20fund%20under%20the%20EPFO.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fepfo-data-with-13-3-dip-in-new-monthly-subscribers-formal-job-creation-slowed-in-august%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22ICICI%20Bank%20Q2%20results%3A%20Net%20profit%20jumps%2036%25%20to%20Rs%2010%2C261%20cr%2C%20NII%20up%2024%25%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697887786000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-09%2F28%2Ffull%2F1695883865-6682.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Ficici-bank-q2-results-net-profit-jumps-36-to-rs-10-261-cr-nii-up-24-123102100512_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20total%20income%20in%20the%20second%20quarter%20of%20the%20current%20fiscal%20rose%20to%20Rs%2040%2C697%20crore%20from%20Rs%2031%2C088%20crore%20in%20the%20same%20period%20a%20year%20ago%2C%20ICICI%20Bank%20said%20in%20a%20regulatory%20filing%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Ficici-bank-q2-results-net-profit-jumps-36-to-rs-10-261-cr-nii-up-24-123102100512_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Ficici-bank-q2-results-net-profit-jumps-36-to-rs-10-261-cr-nii-up-24-123102100512_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Ficici-bank-q2-results-net-profit-jumps-36-to-rs-10-261-cr-nii-up-24-123102100512_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%20%7C%20'This%20Gaza%20Bloodbath%20Must%20Immediately%20Be%20Stopped'%3A%20Haaretz%20Columnist%20Gideon%20Levy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F21163011%2F5ef6b2e8-e5e1-4162-9732-877144619655.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20boldest%20voices%20in%20Israel%20has%20spoken%20out%20in%20strong%20terms%20demanding%20an%20immediate%20end%20to%20the%20continuing%20Israeli%20airstrikes%20over%20Gaza%20and%20adding%20that%20the%20allegedly%20imminent%20ground%20invasion%20must%20not%20happen%20at%20all%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGideon%20Levy%2C%20the%20internationally%20acclaimed%20columnist%20for%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EHaaretz%3C%2Fem%3E%20newspaper%2C%20says%20that%20Israel%20and%20the%20world%20must%20accept%20that%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20two-state%20solution%20is%20dead%20and%20impossible%20to%20revive.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20he%20says%2C%20the%20only%20feasible%20solution%20is%20a%20one-state%20solution%20where%20Israelis%20and%20Arabs%2C%20Jews%20and%20Muslims%20have%20equal%20rights.%20Although%20neither%20politicians%20nor%20public%20opinion%20in%20Israel%20are%20ready%20to%20accept%20this%2C%20Levy%20says%20they%20have%20to%20realise%2C%20no%20doubt%20with%20time%2C%20that%20this%20is%20the%20only%20solution.%20He%20also%20says%20that%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20Western%20friends%2C%20particularly%20America%2C%20must%20start%20pushing%20them%20in%20this%20direction.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20this%20is%20the%20opposite%20of%20the%20message%20President%20Biden%20delivered%20when%20he%20visited%20Israel%20earlier%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F0GnGC3yPYwk%3Fsi%3DQ9Nn4NooQzuc8_8O%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3ELevy%20says%20there%20have%20to%20be%20limits%20to%20the%20devastation%20and%20that%20although%20%E2%80%9Cit%E2%80%99s%20impossible%20to%20let%20(what%20Hamas%20did)%20pass%20without%20settling%20accounts%E2%80%9D%20nonetheless%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthere%E2%80%99s%20a%20vast%20middle%20ground%20between%20doing%20nothing%20and%20massive%20bloodshed%20that%20has%20no%20point%20or%20purpose%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELevy%20says%20the%20present%20airstrikes%2C%20which%20are%20continuing%20not%20just%20in%20the%20north%20but%20also%20in%20the%20south%20of%20Gaza%2C%20which%20was%20supposed%20to%20a%20safe%20area%2C%20with%2053%20people%20killed%20overnight%2C%20have%20%E2%80%9Cno%20clear%20realistic%20purpose%20and%20certainly%20no%20answer%20to%20the%20question%20of%20what%20happens%20on%20the%20day%20after.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20also%20concerned%20that%20this%20continuing%20bombing%20of%20Gaza%20could%20have%20a%20terrible%20impact%20on%20the%20people%20of%20Israel%20themselves.%20He%20says%20%E2%80%9CEven%20in%20the%20heat%20of%20our%20anger%20and%20frustration%2C%20we%20must%20not%20lose%20whatever%20remains%20of%20our%20conscience%20and%20moral%20compass.%20We%20must%20not%20let%20all%20of%20Israel%20become%20Hamas.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20ground%20invasion%2C%20which%20is%20believed%20to%20be%20imminent%2C%20Levy%20adds%20this%20would%20exacerbate%20the%20problem%2C%20possibly%20even%20resulting%20in%20a%20world%20war.%20A%20ground%20invasion%20that%20kills%20hundreds%20or%20thousands%20of%20Palestinians%20and%2C%20perhaps%2C%20tens%20or%20hundreds%20of%20Israeli%20soldiers%2C%20is%20likely%20to%20provoke%20Hizbullah%20and%20even%20Iran%20to%20enter%20the%20conflict.%20That%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20could%20lead%20to%20American%20intervention.%20And%2C%20as%20Levy%20put%20it%2C%20this%20could%20lead%20to%20a%20world%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Levy%20dismissed%20the%20possibility%20raised%20by%20Yuval%20Noah%20Harari%20in%20a%20recent%20%3Cem%3EWashington%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%20op-ed%20that%2C%20if%20critically%20pushed%2C%20Israel%20could%20use%20the%20atom%20bomb.%20Levy%20said%20the%20ground%20invasion%20must%20not%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWatch%20the%20interview%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0GnGC3yPYwk%3Ffeature%3Dshared%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697886861000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F21163011%2F5ef6b2e8-e5e1-4162-9732-877144619655.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fvideo-gid