ical%20education%20in%20the%20country%2C%20said%20that%20it%20has%20learned%20%E2%80%9Cabout%20the%20conduct%20of%20UG%20(undergraduate)%20MBBS%20counseling%20(both%20through%20online%20and%20offline%20mode)%20by%20several%20states%20(such%20as%20the%20state%20of%20Maharashtra%2C%20Bihar%2C%20West%20Bengal%2C%20etc.)%20beyond%20the%20cut-off%20date%20of%20September%2030.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENMC%20reiterated%20that%20by%20means%20of%20a%20public%20notice%20on%20July%2027%2C%20it%20had%20informed%20all%20stakeholders%20about%20the%20cut-off%20date%20for%20conducting%20the%20counselling%20sessions%20and%20therefore%2C%20%E2%80%9Cany%20admission%20or%20conduct%20of%20counselling%20beyond%20the%20cut-off%20date%20is%20in%20violation%20of%20the%20notice%20issued%20by%20NMC%20as%20well%20as%20in%20violation%20of%20the%20judgements%20passed%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202016%2C%20the%20apex%20court%20had%20fixed%20the%20time%20schedule%20for%20processing%20of%20the%20admission%20of%20not%20just%20the%20UG%20MBBS%20course%20but%20also%20for%20post%20graduate%20and%20super-specialty%20medical%20and%20dental%20courses%20after%20consulting%20all%20state%20and%20union%20territories%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20and%20other%20stakeholders.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAsking%20all%20stakeholders%20to%20therefore%20%E2%80%9Cstrictly%20adhere%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20counselling%20session%20fixed%20by%20the%20NMC%20for%20the%20academic%20session%20of%202023-24%20for%20the%20undergraduate%20MBBS%20course%2C%20the%20notification%20issued%20by%20Shambhu%20Sharan%20Kumar%2C%20director%20of%20undergraduate%20medical%20education%20board%2C%20said%20the%20admissions%20of%20who%20were%20accommodated%20after%20the%20September%2030%20deadline%20would%20be%20declared%20invalid%20and%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20students%20admitted%2C%20if%20any%2C%20shall%20be%20discharged%20immediately%E2%80%9D.%20%3C%2Fsp