%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F104607819.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20biographical%20film%20%26quot%3BMain%20Atal%20Hoon%26quot%3B%20about%20the%20late%20Shri%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20is%20facing%20a%20legal%20dispute%20involving%20key%20stakeholders%20such%20as%20Sandeep%20Singh%2C%20Vinod%20Bhanushali%2C%2070MM%20Talkies%2C%20Penguin%20India%2C%20and%20the%20author%20Ullekh%20Np.%20The%20film%2C%20adapted%20from%20Ullekh%20Np's%20book%2C%20has%20encountered%20challenges%20including%20profit-sharing%20issues.%20The%20case%20is%20currently%20being%20heard%20in%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court%2C%20with%20the%20next%20hearing%20scheduled%20for%20October%2026th%2C%202023.%20The%20controversy%20surrounding%20Sandeep%20Singh's%20film%20%26quot%3BSawarkar%26quot%3B%20has%20also%20affected%20%26quot%3BMain%20Atal%20Hoon.%26quot%3B%20The%20release%20and%20future%20of%20the%20biopic%20are%20uncertain%20due%20to%20the%20legal%20dispute.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Flegal-dispute-surrounding-main-atal-hoon-biopic-on-atal-bihari-vajpayee-casts-doubt-on-films-release%2Farticleshow%2F104607819.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pakistan's%20Former%20PM%20Nawaz%20Sharif%20Returns%20Home%20from%20Exile%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F21155724%2FDeath_anniversary_of_Fazil_Rahoo-e1697884729243.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EPakistan%E2%80%99s%20former%20prime%20minister%20Nawaz%20Sharif%20returned%20to%20the%20country%20on%20Saturday%2C%20after%20four%20years%20of%20self-imposed%20exile%20in%20London%2C%20to%20restart%20his%20political%20journey%20ahead%20of%20the%20general%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESharif%E2%80%99s%20return%20comes%20as%20the%20country%20struggles%20with%20high%20inflation%20and%20ot