ion%20%E2%80%9Cfoolproof%E2%80%9D%20a%20senior%20GRP%20official%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20their%20investigation%20has%20found%20out%20that%2033-year-old%20Chaudhary%20was%20fully%20aware%20of%20the%20outcome%20of%20his%20act.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%9CYet%20he%20pressed%20the%20trigger%20and%20killed%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20officer%2C%20privy%20to%20the%20investigation%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20part%20of%20the%20shocking%20incident%2C%20video-graphed%20by%20fellow%20passengers%2C%20showed%20how%20Chaudhary%20went%20on%20firing%20at%20three%20passengers%E2%80%94all%20Muslim%20men%20with%20beards%20%E2%80%93%20across%20nine%20carriages.%20The%20three%20passengers%20%E2%80%93%20Abdul%20Kadar%20Mohamed%20Hussain%20Bhanpurawala%2C%20Syed%20Saifuddin%2C%20and%20Asgar%20Abbas%20Sheikh%20%E2%80%93%20had%20died%20right%20at%20the%20spot.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHis%20senior%20ASI%20Tika%20Ram%20Meena%2C%20the%20investigation%20shows%2C%20was%20killed%20by%20Chaudhary%20after%20he%20was%20denied%20leave%20from%20duty%20on%20the%20fateful%20night.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20police%20claim%20that%20while%20Meena%20could%20have%20been%20killed%20out%20of%20anger%2C%20the%20rest%20three%20killings%20were%20selective%20in%20nature.%20Both%20Meena%20and%20Chaudhary%20were%20deployed%20in%20the%20train%20for%20security.%20And%20the%20investigation%20shows%20that%20the%20firing%20incident%20took%20place%20soon%20after%20an%20argument%20between%20Kumar%20and%20Ram%20broke%20out.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20the%20witnesses%2C%20a%20passenger%2C%20has%20claimed%20that%20Chaudhary%20had%20also%20forced%20a%20burqa-clad%20passenger%20to%20chant%20%E2%80%98Jai%20Mata%20Di%E2%80%99%20at%20a%20gunpoint.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20purported%20video%2C%20which%20the%20police%20have%20now%20used%20as%20a%20crucial%20piece%20of%20evidence%2C%20Chaudhary%20could%20be%20seen%20speaking%20to%20passengers%20while%20standing%20over%20Asghar%E2%80%99s%20bloodied%20body.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChaudhary%20is%20heard%20saying%3A%20%E2%80%9CPakistan%20%3Cem%3Ese%20operate%20hue%20hain%2C%20tumhari%3C%2Fem%3E%20media%2C%20%3Cem%3Eyahi%3C%2Fem%3E%20media%20coverage%20%3Cem%3Edikha%20rahi%20hai%20hai%2C%20pata%20chal%20raha%20hai%20unko%2C%20sab%20pata%20chal%20raha%20hai%2C%20inke%20aaqa%20hai%20wahan%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%A6%20%3Cem%3EAgar%3C%2Fem%3E%20vote%20%3Cem%3Edena%20hai%2C%20agar%20%3C%2Fem%3EHindustan%3Cem%3E%20me%20rehna%20hai%2C%20toh%20mai%20kehta%20hoon%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20Modi%20%3Cem%3Eaur%20%3C%2Fem%3EYogi%3Cem%3E%2C%20ye%20do%20hain%2C%20aur%20aapke%20%3C%2Fem%3EThackeray.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E(%E2%80%98They%20operate%20from%20Pakistan%2C%20this%20is%20what%20the%20media%20of%20the%20country%20is%20showing%2C%20they%20have%20found%20out%2C%20they%20know%20everything%2C%20their%20leaders%20are%20there%E2%80%A6%20If%20you%20want%20to%20vote%2C%20if%20you%20want%20to%20live%20in%20India%2C%20then%20I%20say%2C%20Modi%20and%20Yogi%2C%20these%20are%20the%20two%2C%20and%20your%20Thackeray%E2%80%99)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0At%20the%20time%20of%20submitting%20the%20charge%20sheet%20before%20the%20Borivali%20metropolitan%20magistrate%20court%2C%20the%20GRP%20told%20the%20court%20that%20Chaudhary%20was%20not%20brought%20to%20the%20court%20but%20produced%20through%20video%20conferencing%20as%20it%20might%20not%20be%20safe%20for%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInitially%2C%20the%20railways%20had%20harped%20on%20Chaudhary%E2%80%99s%20mental%20health%20but%20had%20eventually%20termed%20his%20act%20as%20a%20heinous%20crime.%20He%20was%20dismissed%20from%20service%20in%20the%20month%20of%20August.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESoon%20after%20the%20incident%2C%20Chaudhary%20was%20booked%20under%20Section%20302%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20for%20murder%2C%20along%20with%20sections%20of%20the%20Arms%20Act%20and%20the%20Indian%20Railways%20Act.%20At%20the%20time%20of%20his%20first%20production%20before%20a%20magistrate%20court%20on%20August%202%2C%20the%20police%20had%20chosen%20a%20diametrically%20opposite%20narrative%20to%20what%20was%20in%20the%20public%20domain.%20The%20remand%20copy%20did%20not%20make%20any%20mention%20of%20the%20video%20that%20clearly%20showed%20his%20communally-charged%20speech.%20The%20remand%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20entirely%20focused%20on%20Chaudhary%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cillness%E2%80%9D%20and%20indicates%20his%20unstable%20mind%20which%20led%20him%20to%20conduct%20the%20extreme%20action.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fpolice-focuses-on-rpf-constables-mental-illness-erases-mention-of-possible-hate-crime-from-fir%5C%22%3EPolice%20Focuses%20on%20RPF%20Constable%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Mental%20Illness%E2%80%99%2C%20Erases%20Mention%20of%20Possible%20Hate%20Crime%20from%20FIR%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20few%20days%20later%2C%20following%20criticism%2C%20the%20police%20had%20added%20sections%20153A%2C%20341%20and%20342%20of%20the%20IPC%20and%20151%2C%20152%20and%20153%20of%20Indian%20Railways%20Act.%20Section%20153%20A%20is%20for%20%E2%80%9Cpromoting%20enmity%20between%20different%20groups%20on%20grounds%20of%20religion%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20chargesheet%2C%20the%20police%20have%20now%20added%20sections%20like%20364%20(kidnapping%20for%20murder)%2C%20427%20(mischief%20and%20causing%20loss)%2C%20506%20(2)%20(death%20threats)%20of%20the%20IPC%20and%20Section%203%20of%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Damage%20to%20Public%20Property%20Act.%20Although%20Meena%2C%20who%20belongs%20to%20the%20Adivasi%20community%20from%20Rajasthan%2C%20was%20killed%20in%20the%20attack%2C%20sections%20of%20the%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20the%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(Prevention%20of%20Atrocities)%20Act%20have%20not%20been%20applied%20in%20the%20case.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20police%20claim%20that%20they%20have%20managed%20a%20good%20number%20of%20both%20direct%20and%20circumstantial%20witnesses%20in%20the%20case.%20The%20case%20is%20next%20scheduled%20for%20hearing%20on%20November%202.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697875422000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2F16111107%2F5264934981_08748b0f32_k.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fgovernment-railway-police-rpf-bjp-mental-illness%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20police%20claimed%20that%20while%20senior%20ASI%20Tika%20Ram%20Meena%20could%20have%20been%20killed%20out%20of%20anger%2C%20the%20murders%20of%20the%20three%20Muslim%20men%20were%20selective%20in%20nature.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fgovernment-railway-police-rpf-bjp-mental-illness%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%223%20IAS%20Officers%20Share%20Tips%20On%20How%20Smart%20Revision%20Helped%20Them%20Crack%20UPSC%20CSE%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEvery%20year%2C%20thousands%20of%20aspirants%20write%20one%20of%20the%20most%20competitive%20examinations%20UPSC%2C%20but%20only%20a%20few%20make%20it%20to%20the%20final%20list%20with%20a%20good%20score.%20IAS%20officers%20say%20smart%20revision%20is%20the%20ultimate%20key%20to%20managing%20a%20good%20score.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20IAS%20officers%20share%20revision%20techniques%20that%20aspirants%20could%20adopt.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20typical%20day%20for%20an%20aspirant%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIAS%20Officer%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F229686%2Fupsc-cse-prelims-2020-ias-topper-tips-last-minute-revision-general-studies-vid01%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENaveen%20Kumar%20Chandra%3C%2Fa%3E%20clinched%20an%20All%20India%20Rank%20of%20490%20in%20the%20Civil%20Service%20Examination%20(CSE)%202017.%20He%20says%20aspirants%20should%20revise%20at%20least%2015%20to%2020%20days%E2%80%99%20worth%20of%20current%20affairs%20daily%2C%20and%20each%20day%2C%20they%20must%20also%20pick%20one%20subject%20from%20the%20general%20studies%20paper%20to%20revise%20thoroughly.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMinimum%20syllabus%2C%20maximum%20revision%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F307829%2Frevision-tips-for-upsc-cse-mains-optional-subject-by-ias-officer-akshita-gupta%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIAS%20Akshita%20Gupta%3C%2Fa%3E%20secured%20an%20All%20India%20Rank%20of%2069%20in%20UPSC%202020.%20She%20scored%20299%20out%20of%20500%20in%20her%20optional%20subject%20of%20medical%20science%20because%20of%20smart%20revision.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20revision%20gap%20causes%20a%20loss%20of%20memory.%20Since%20the%20syllabus%20is%20vast%2C%20one%20should%20revise%20topics%20frequently%20so%20as%20not%20to%20get%20overwhelmed.%20I%20scored%20well%20in%20my%20optional%20because%20I%20used%20to%20revise%20daily.%20Smart%20revision%20is%20the%20ultimate%20key%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAkshita%20suggests%20jotting%20down%20important%20facts%20about%20every%20topic%20in%20a%20clean%20thin%20register.%20This%20helps%20to%20revise%20a%20day%20before%20the%20exam%20and%20retain%20facts%20about%20almost%20every%20topic.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%20start%20your%20day%2C%20revise%20what%20you%20learnt%20the%20previous%20day.%20It%20is%20not%20time-consuming%20and%20also%20helps%20you%20retain%20knowledge.%20Keep%20your%20syllabus%20minimum%2C%20but%20revision%20maximum%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20IAS%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead-revise-rectify-repeat%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIAS%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F269105%2Fias-himanshu-gupta-cracked-upsc-cse-without-coaching-inspiring%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHimanshu%20Gupta%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20cleared%20the%20UPSC%20thrice%2C%20most%20recently%20in%202020%20with%20an%20All%20India%20Rank%20of%20139%2C%20without%20resorting%20to%20any%20formal%20coaching%2C%20advises%20aspirants%20to%20read%20less%20and%20revise%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20says%20that%20unless%20one%20revises%20enough%20times%2C%20any%20sort%20of%20preparation%20for%20the%20UPSC%20CSE%20is%20pointless.%20%E2%80%9CKeep%20your%20sources%20fixed%20and%20ensure%20you%20follow%20a%20simple%20technique%20of%20read-revise-rectify-repeat.%20This%20will%20ensure%20you%20are%20well%20prepared%20to%20tackle%20the%20examination%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697874300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D332617%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Three%20IAS%20officers%20share%20their%20tried-and-tested%20revision%20techniques%20for%20UPSC%20CSE%20aspirants%20who%20are%20looking%20for%20tips%20to%20prepare%20well%20for%20the%20examination.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332617%2Fias-officers-share-revision-tips-tricks-techniques-upsc-cse-aspirants%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Two%20US%20Citizens%20Freed%20from%20Hamas's%20Captivity%2C%20Over%20200%20Still%20Held%20Hostage%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F21125808%2FThe-Wire-45.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delh