i-efforts-2023-10-20%2F%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20Reuters%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Israel%2C%20203%20people%20were%20abducted%20by%20Hamas%20following%20the%20October%207%20attack.%20Besides%20Israelis%2C%20citizens%20of%20Thailand%2C%20Argentina%2C%20Germany%2C%20France%2C%20and%20Portugal%20are%20under%20Hamas%E2%80%99%20captivity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%C2%A0Hamas%20group%20said%20it%20was%20working%20with%20Qatar%20and%20Egypt%20to%20free%20its%20%E2%80%9Ccivilian%E2%80%9D%20hostages%2C%20in%20a%20sign%20that%20they%20would%20release%20more%20people%20soon.%20It%20also%20said%2050%20more%20captives%20are%20held%20by%20other%20armed%20groups%20in%20Gaza%2C%20adding%20that%20more%20than%2020%20were%20killed%20by%20Israeli%20air%20strikes%20without%20sharing%20any%20further%20details%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-war-gaza-palestine-news-updates-hamas-frees-two-us-hostages-more-releases-likely-soon-4501626%5C%22%3ENDTV%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOfficials%20from%20the%20US%20and%20Britain%20said%20they%20have%20been%20in%20talks%20with%20Qatar%20and%20Egypt%20to%20secure%20the%20release%20of%20their%20citizens%20from%20hostage.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Israel%2C%20Judith%20Tai%20Raanan%20and%20Natalie%20were%20abducted%20from%20Kibbutz%20Nahal%20Oz%20in%20southern%20Israel.%20The%20mother-daughter%20duo%20from%20Illinois%20landed%20in%20Israel%20in%20September%20to%20celebrate%20the%20Jewish%20holidays%2C%20Natalie%E2%80%99s%20high%20school%20graduation%2C%20and%20the%2085th%20birthday%20of%20her%20grandmother.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697873667000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F21125808%2FThe-Wire-45.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Ftwo-us-citizens-walk-free-from-hamass-captivity-over-200-still-held-hostage%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22According%20to%20Israel%2C%20203%20people%20were%20abducted%20by%20Hamas%20following%20October%207%20attack.%20Qatar%20and%20Egypt%20are%20mediating%20between%20Hamas%20and%20Israel%20to%20secure%20the%20release%20of%20others%20held%20hostage.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Ftwo-us-citizens-walk-free-from-hamass-captivity-over-200-still-held-hostage%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Interview%20%7C%20'BJP%20Keeps%20Fishing'%3A%20Chhattisgarh%20Dy%20CM%20T.S.%20Singh%20Deo%20on%20'Rifts'%20With%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F21124231%2FF62XnN6WEAA2dJU-e1697872424177.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmid%20questions%20of%20alleged%20differences%20between%20Chhattisgarh%20chief%20minister%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%20and%20his%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20T.S%20Singh%20Deo%2C%20the%20latter%20has%20said%20that%20while%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20keeps%20%E2%80%9Cfishing%E2%80%9D%20with%20the%20goal%20of%20cashing%20in%20on%20such%20rifts%2C%20for%20him%2C%20there%20has%20never%20been%20any%20question%20of%20joining%20the%20saffron%20party.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20telephonic%20interview%20with%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3ESingh%20Deo%20addresses%20the%20big%20issues%20in%20this%20election%20where%20the%20Congress%20is%20looking%20to%20return%20to%20power%20after%20trouncing%20the%20BJP%20in%202018.%20He%20also%20addresses%20the%20corruption%20allegations%20raised%20against%20his%20government%20by%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EExcerpts%20of%20the%20chat%20are%20below.%20Some%20answers%20have%20been%20shortened%20for%20length.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ECongress%20is%20contesting%20on%20the%20slogan%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EPhir%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3ESe%3C%2Fem%3E%20Congress%20%3Cem%3ESarkar%20%3C%2Fem%3E(once%20again%20a%20Congress%20government)%E2%80%99.%20What%20are%20the%20issues%20that%20you%20will%20be%20highlighting%20this%20election%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhatever%20we%20had%20talked%20about%20before%20the%20elections%20and%20whatever%20we%20have%20been%20able%20to%20deliver%2C%20that%20will%20be%20our%20plank%20for%20seeking%20the%20support%20of%20the%20people%20again.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENowhere%20in%20the%20country%20are%20paddy%20farmers%20getting%20as%20much%20value%20for%20their%20crops%20as%20in%20Chhattisgarh.%20We%20had%20assured%20that%20we%20would%20be%20waiving%20short%20term%20farm%20loans%2C%20which%20we%20did%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20about%20Rs%2010%2C000%20crores.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20assured%20the%20farmers%20that%20we%20would%20purchase%20paddy%20at%20least%20at%20Rs%202500%2Fquintal.%20And%20now%20we%20will%20be%20purchasing%20paddy%20at%20just%20short%20of%20Rs%202800%20in%20November.%20As%20far%20as%20sugarcane%20is%20concerned%20we%20had%20assured%20them%20a%20minimum%20price%20of%20355%2Fquintal%20today%20they%20are%20getting%20at%20over%20Rs%20400.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20had%20assured%20labourers%20engaged%20in%20collecting%20beedi%20leaves%20in%20the%20tribal%20forest%20areas%2C%20that%20we%20will%20increase%20the%20rates%20from%20Rs%202%2C500%20to%20Rs%204%2C000.%20As%20far%20as%20other%20forest%20produce%20is%20concerned%2C%20there%20was%20earlier%20a%20regime%20of%20seven%20forest%20produce%20which%20were%20to%20be%20purchased%20at%20MSP%20by%20the%20central%20government.%20They%20withdrew%20that%20notification.%20Today%20through%20the%20state%20government%20we%20are%20being%20able%20to%20assure%20them%20of%20procuring%2067%20forest%20produce%20at%20MSP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChhattisgarh%20today%20is%20the%20leading%20state%20in%20the%20country%20contributing%20to%20about%2072%20to%2074%25%20of%20the%20total%20forest%20produce%20in%20the%20country.%20This%20is%20money%20that%20is%20going%20straight%20into%20the%20pockets%20of%20the%20people.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20had%20promised%20and%20delivered%20on%20giving%20electricity%20up%20to%20400%20units%20at%20half%20the%20rate.%20We%20are%20providing%20electricity%20to%20farmers%20at%20their%20irrigation%20pumps%20and%20free%20of%20cost%20to%20Scheduled%20Caste%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20farmers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20have%20been%20providing%20health%20cover%20up%20to%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20for%20a%20family%20in%20a%20year.%20Where%20education%20is%20concerned%20we%20have%20opened%20Swami%20Atmanand%20English%20medium%20schools.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20also%20have%20doorstep%20delivery%20of%20services%2C%20which%20is%20also%20perhaps%20in%20other%20states%20too.%20In%20addition%20we%20have%20provided%20an%20unemployment%20allowance%20to%20students.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20had%20not%20been%20able%20to%20take%20up%20housing%20%E2%80%93%20which%20we%20had%20promised%20%E2%80%93%20due%20to%20financial%20restraints.%20We%20were%20not%20able%20to%20provide%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Awas%20Yojana.%20Despite%20the%20central%20government%20withdrawing%20its%20funding%20from%20that%20temporarily%20we%20have%20asked%20them%20to%20come%20forward%20with%20their%20contribution.%20Even%20if%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20we%20have%20already%20announced%20that%20we%20will%20provide%20this%20through%20DBT%20transfers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EIn%20a%20recent%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Finterview-chhattisgarh-election-raman-singh-bjp-chief-minister-face%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3Einterview%20with%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cb%3E%3Ci%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cb%3E%20former%20CM%20Raman%20Singh%20said%20that%20the%20BJP%20will%20make%20corruption%20the%20biggest%20issue%20in%20these%20elections%20and%20highlight%20the%20liquor%20scam%2C%20loan%20scam%2C%20coal%20levy%20scam%2C%20and%20so%20on.%20Do%20you%20see%20corruption%20being%20a%20big%20issue%20and%20can%20it%20work%20against%20the%20party%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFirst%20Mr%20Raman%20Singh%20should%20be%20answering%20about%20the%20scam%20which%20had%20taken%20place%20while%20he%20was%20chief%20minister%2C%20which%20was%20the%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fchhattisgarh-nan-pds-scam-ed-judge-accused-touch%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Rs%2036%2C000%20crore%20PDS%20scam.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20were%20so%20many%20other%20things%20that%20had%20come%20up%20while%20he%20was%20chief%20minister%20and%20not%20one%20was%20enquired%20by%20the%20ED%20or%20the%20IT.%20That%20apart%2C%20who%20in%20the%20government%20%E2%80%93%20as%20far%20as%20elected%20representatives%20are%20concerned%20%E2%80%93%20has%20been%20booked%3F%20Some%20government%20officers%20have%20been%20found%20guilty%20and%20we%20have%20always%20maintained%20that%20whoever%20is%20found%20guilty%20you%20take%20action.%20Today%20even%20the%20home%20minister%20comes%20and%20makes%20allegations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20are%20in%20a%20position%20to%20make%20enquiries%20and%20take%20action.%20It%20is%20now%20known%20in%20the%20country%20that%20if%20you%20are%20in%20the%20opposition%20ED%2C%20IT%20comes%20knocking%20and%20the%20moment%20you%20switch%20parties%20no%20action%20is%20taken.%20So%20it%20is%20more%20than%20clear%20that%20nothing%20but%20misuse%20of%20these%20agencies%20is%20being%20done%20against%20the%20opposition.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F14140422%2FScreenshot-2023-10-14-at-2.04.16%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22988%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F14140422%2FScreenshot-2023-10-14-at-2.04.16%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%20988w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F14140422%2FScreenshot-2023-10-14-at-2.04.16%25E2%2580%25AFPM-300x152.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-680081%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22502%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERaman%20Singh.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40drramansingh%2FVideo%20screengrab.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EBJP%20has%20also%20raised%20questions%20about%20infighting%20in%20the%20Chhattisgarh%20Congress.%20Recently%20after%20you%20thanked%20the%20PM%20at%20an%20event%20for%20all%20the%20central%20projects%20announced%20in%20the%20state%2C%20Raman%20Singh%20said%20you%20were%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fts-singh-deo-forced-to-apologise-for-praising-pm-raman-singh%2Farticle67323409.ece%23%3A~%3Atext%3DWhile%2520Chhattisgarh%2520Deputy%2520Chief%2520Minister%2Cin%2520no%2520mood%2520to%2520relent.%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3Eforced%20to%20apologise%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cb%3E.%20Are%20there%20any%20differences%20between%20you%20and%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20people%20don%E2%80%99t%20understand%20courtesy%20and%20want%20to%20make%20politics%20then%20they%20are%20welcome%20to%20go%20ahead.%20There%20have%20been%20any%20number%20of%20occasions%20when%20on%20a%20political%20platform%20we%20have%20rightly%20spoken%20up%20against%20many%20of%20the%20actions%20taken%20by%20the%20prime%20minister%20and%20the%20(Union)%20government%20which%20has%20put%20the%20country%20into%20so%20many%20difficulties%2C%20whether%20it%20was%20demonetisation%20or%20GST%20implementation%20or%20the%20border%20situation%20or%20where%20Manipur%20is%20burning.%20So%20where%20have%20we%20not%20brought%20these%20matters%20to%20the%20attention%20of%20the%20country%20at%20large%3F%20Whether%20it%20is%20me%20or%20otherwise.%20So%20a%20nicety%20when%20you%20are%20at%20a%20government%20function%20to%20a%20guest%20who%20has%20come%20in%20a%20federal%20structure%20where%20you%20need%20to%20mend%20relationships%20and%20see%20the%20best%20interests%20of%20your%20state%20small%20and%20petty%20things%20don%E2%80%99t%20come%20in%20the%20way.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20we%20are%20on%20a%20political%20platform%20we%20bring%20up%20these%20things%2C%20but%20on%20a%20government%20platform%20there%20are%20niceties%20to%20be%20maintained%20and%20we%20maintain%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20CM%20said%20the%20same%20thing%20when%20he%20asked%20me%20to%20represent%20the%20state%20when%20the%20prime%20minister%20was%20coming.%20The%20health%20department%20had%20some%20schemes%20which%20were%20talked%20about%20on%20the%20platform%20so%20I%20welcomed%20him%20as%20a%20public%20representative%20of%20a%20federal%20unit%20of%20our%20country.%20We%20were%20representing%20our%20state%20and%20he%20was%20representing%20the%20central%20government.%20If%20you%20want%20to%20play%20politics%20on%20that%20you%20are%20welcome.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EHas%20anyone%20from%20the%20BJP%20been%20in%20touch%20with%20you%20as%20they%20look%20to%20perhaps%20cash%20in%20on%20these%20alleged%20differences%20with%20CM%20Baghel%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWere%20the%20BJP%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20government%20in%20Maharashtra%E2%80%99s%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20including%20NCP%20and%20others%3F%20Were%20they%20or%20were%20they%20not%20in%20touch%3F%20So%20they%20keep%20fishing%20if%20they%20feel%20that%20there%20is%20something%20that%20they%20might%20be%20able%20to%20cash%20in%20on.%20Since%20ideology%20does%20not%20have%20any%20meaning%20in%20their%20dictionary%20or%20maybe%20general%20dictionary%20of%20politics%20sadly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20I%20have%20always%20said%20very%20clearly%20that%20there%20is%20never%20any%20question%20of%20ever%20joining%20the%20BJP%20or%20any%20other%20party.%20There%20has%20never%20been%20any%20question%20of%20ever%20joining%20the%20BJP%20because%20there%20are%20basic%20ideological%20differences%20which%20a%20small%20humble%20person%20like%20me%20will%20never%20be%20able%20to%20cross.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F21124421%2FF5gePirW4AAqwSk.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F21124421%2FF5gePirW4AAqwSk.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F21124421%2FF5gePirW4AAqwSk-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F21124421%2FF5gePirW4AAqwSk-1024x683.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681147%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESingh%20Deo%20with%20Chhattisgarh%20CM%20Bhupesh%20Baghel.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40TS_SinghDeo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EBut%20they%20have%20been%20fishing%20with%20you%20then%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENot%20very%20recently%2C%20but%20certainly%20at%20other%20times.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThere%20have%20been%20various%20instances%20of%20anti-Christian%20violence%20reported%20from%20across%20various%20villages%20in%20Bastar.%20D%3C%2Fb%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fchhattisgarh-attacks-christians-congress-minority-rights%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3Eata%20collected%20by%20the%20United%20Christian%20Forum%20in%202022%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cb%3E%20says%20that%20after%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20(99)%2C%20the%20second%20highest%20number%20of%20cases%20were%20reported%20from%20Chhattisgarh%20(89).%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EHow%20do%20you%20plan%20to%20address%20this%20amid%20rising%20concerns%20about%20the%20Congress%20government%20not%20being%20serious%20about%20minorities%E2%80%99%20safety%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20chief%20minister%20has%20been%20very%20clear%20on%20this%20matter%20that%20action%20will%20be%20taken%20on%20merit.%20And%20action%20has%20been%20taken%20against%20many%20people%2C%20those%20reports%20are%20perhaps%20not%20being%20put%20out%20in%20the%20media%20where%20people%20are%20behind%20jail%20for%20indulging%20in%20these%20actions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20being%20done%20through%20RSS%20organisations%20as%20they%20are%20doing%20in%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20where%20they%20are%20trying%20to%20create%20a%20rift%20between%20the%20people%20and%20trying%20to%20put%20across%20majoritarian%20sentiment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20absolutely%20true%20that%20these%20vitiated%20minds%20are%20indulging%20in%20not%20allowing%20burial%20of%20the%20dead%20of%20people%20of%20christian%20community%20in%20certain%20districts%20in%20Bastar%20in%20Narayanpur%2C%20Bijapur%2C%20and%20others.%20In%20a%20very%20targeted%20way%20they%20are%20trying%20to%20create%20fissures%20to%20create%20a%20majoritarian%20sentiment%20but%20they%20will%20fail%20because%20the%20government%20is%20completely%20even%20handed%20and%20whoever%20takes%20law%20and%20order%20into%20their%20hands%2C%20action%20will%20be%20taken%20against%20them%20and%20has%20been%20taken%20already.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EBJP%20has%20also%20made%20the%20claim%20of%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fraipur%2Fmass-conversions-in-chhattisgarh-under-congress-govt-amit-shah%2Farticleshow%2F103315610.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%98forced%20conversions%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cb%3E%20a%20big%20issue%20in%20Chhattisgarh.%20Amit%20Shah%20has%20also%20accused%20the%20Congress%20of%20it%20in%20tribal%20areas.%20How%20would%20you%20respond%20to%20this%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAgain%2C%20an%20accusation.%20Has%20he%20given%20the%20name%20which%20individual%20and%20where%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20has%20been%20converted%20has%20he%20given%20a%20name%3F%20These%20are%20baseless%20allegations%20and%20in%20fact%20there%20were%20far%20more%20conversions%20during%20the%20BJP%20government.%20Even%20then%20it%20was%20minimal%20but%20it%20was%20far%20more%20than%20what%20it%20is%20now.%20We%20want%20names%2C%20not%20allegations.%20He%20is%20the%20home%20minister%20of%20the%20country%2C%20he%20should%20be%20having%20names.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EChhattisgarh%20has%20a%20large%20tribal%20population%20of%20about%2030%25.%20What%20will%20be%20your%20government%E2%80%99s%20outlook%20on%20their%20welfare%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20that%20I%20mentioned%20earlier%2C%20about%20forest%20produce%2C%20beedi%20leaves%2C%2067%20other%20forest%20produce%20being%20collected%20by%20self%20help%20groups.%20And%20a%20large%20number%20of%20women%20have%20been%20empowered%20through%20value%20addition%20and%20collection%20of%20these%20products.%20Millets%20%E2%80%93%20we%20had%20highlighted%20in%20our%20manifesto%20%E2%80%93%20that%20we%20will%20be%20focusing%20on%20their%20procurement%20and%20today%20we%20are%20purchasing%20that%20on%20MSP.%20Millet%20is%20grown%20on%20less%20fertile%20lands%20which%20lie%20on%20hilly%20terrain%20which%20again%20lie%20in%20the%20tribal%20majority%20belts.%20And%20today%20they%20are%20getting%20very%20good%20remunerative%20prices%20in%20the%20market.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EApart%20from%20this%20education%20infrastructure%2C%20supporting%20their%20cultural%20activities%20through%20local%20coordinates%20through%20the%20government%20through%20cash%20being%20provided%20for%20upkeep%20of%20centres%20of%20religious%20sentiments%2C%20and%20giving%20stipend%20to%20those%20who%20look%20after%20these%20places%20of%20worship%20and%20bringing%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fchhatisgarh-pesa-rules-gujarat-congress%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EPESA%20Act%20(Panchayat%20Extension%20to%20Scheduled%20Areas)%20rules.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20could%20be%20issues%20of%20empowering%20people%20more%20but%20the%20government%20has%20assured%20people%20that%20we%20will%20go%20step%20by%20step.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EAmit%20Shah%20has%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1714928635327795312%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3Esaid%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cb%3E%20that%20Maoist%20presence%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20have%20gone%20down%20during%20the%20BJP%20rule%20at%20the%20Union.%20How%20do%20you%20see%20the%20home%20minister%E2%80%99s%20statement%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIs%20the%20Naxal%20issue%20a%20state%20issue%20or%20central%20issue%3F%20There%20are%20paramilitary%20forces%20that%20have%20been%20posted%20there%2C%20no%20denying%20that.%20We%20are%20in%20a%20federal%20democracy%20not%20by%20one%20government%20run%20from%20the%20centre.%20Law%20and%20order%20which%20deals%20with%20the%20Naxal%20situation%20is%20the%20responsibility%20of%20the%20state%20government.%20The%20chief%20minister%20heads%20the%20joint%20command.%20Mr%20Amit%20Shah%20should%20not%20be%20petty%20to%20take%20the%20credit%20from%20the%20state%20government.%20It%20is%20sad%20that%20they%20want%20to%20take%20credit%20for%20everything.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20Union%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20in%20Chhattisgarh%E2%80%99s%20Kondagaon%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20Congress%20rule%20naxalism%20increased%20while%20the%20BJP%20reduced%20Naxal%20menace%20by%2070%20per%20cent%E2%80%A6Congress%20never%20did%20anything%20for%20the%20development%20of%20the%20tribals%20and%20only%20made%20promises%20which%20were%20never%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F3y8lcHmIZm%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F3y8lcHmIZm%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1714928635327795312%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2019%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EComing%20to%20candidates%2C%20BJP%20has%20decided%20to%20field%20sitting%20Durg%20MP%20Vijay%20Baghel%20from%20the%20Patan%20constituency%20against%20his%20uncle%2C%20chief%20minister%20Bhupesh%20Baghel.%20Several%20other%20MPs%20have%20also%20been%20fielded%20by%20the%20BJP.%20Though%20they%20have%20not%20declared%20a%20CM%20face%20yet%20many%20MPs%20will%20now%20come%20to%20the%20state%20to%20fight%20elections.%20How%20do%20you%20see%20this%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20exposes%20their%20weak%20bench%20strength.%20You%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20people%20who%20can%20fight%20elections%20at%20the%20state%20level.%20That%20is%20the%20first%20message%20that%20I%20get.%20People%20elected%20to%20other%20seats%20of%20representation%2C%20if%20you%20need%20to%20catch%20them%20to%20fight%20state%20elections%20it%20means%20that%20your%20bench%20strength%20is%20very%20weak%20and%20poor.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWith%20Vijay%20Baghel%E2%80%99s%20nomination%2C%20the%20BJP%20seems%20to%20be%20attempting%20to%20woo%20OBC%20voters.%20Is%20this%20going%20to%20affect%20the%20contest%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20are%20trying%20to%20field%20who%20they%20feel%20is%20t