ing%20aerobic%20composting%2C%20the%20major%20challenge%20is%20to%20maintain%20the%20aerobic%20nature%20of%20composting%20which%20gets%20progressively%20difficult%20due%20to%20leaching%20liquid%20and%20size%20reduction%20in%20the%20composting%20material.%20This%20hinders%20the%20free%20passage%20of%20air.%20Bacteria%20cannot%20degrade%20chemicals%20in%20a%20pot.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20tackle%20this%20problem%2C%20he%20has%20developed%20a%20fungal-based%20composting%20inoculum.%20In%20this%2C%20the%20solid%20and%20liquid%20waste%20is%20sandwiched%20between%20spongy%20matrixes.%20Other%20than%20moisture%2C%20the%20matrix%20also%20adsorbs%20stench%20and%20obnoxious%20gases.%20This%20provides%20for%20the%20aerobic%20condition%20when%20waste%20disintegrates%20into%20uniform%20particles%20into%20organic%20manure.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20fungal-based%20inoculum%20completely%20decomposes%20all%20biodegradable%20waste%20into%20soilless%20planting%20media.%20Usually%2C%20we%20add%20100-200%20grams%20of%20compost%20with%20soil%2C%20but%20with%20this%2C%20we%20can%20convert%20thousands%20of%20kgs%20of%20waste%20into%20compost%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Manoj.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20has%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20game-changer%20for%20apartments%20struggling%20with%20waste%20disposal%20challenges.%20About%20200%20apartments%20and%20complexes%20in%20Kerala%20and%20Bengaluru%20have%20begun%20to%20dispose%20of%20their%20solid%20waste%2C%20both%20degradable%20and%20non-degradable%2C%20in%20a%20scientific%20and%20cost-effective%20way%20while%20promoting%20green%20earth.%20For%20this%2C%20Kenterra%20charges%20about%20Rs%20350%20per%20month%20per%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FKenterra-4-1697722661.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Manoj%20informs%20that%20they%20are%20able%20to%20manage%20about%2010%2C000%20kg%20of%20waste%20every%20day.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FKenterra-4-1697722661.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FKenterra-4-1697722661-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FKenterra-4-1697722661-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FKenterra-4-1697722661-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FKenterra-4-1697722661-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-332642%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDr%20Manoj%20informs%20that%20they%20are%20able%20to%20manage%20about%2010%2C000%20kg%20of%20waste%20every%20day.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20these%20housing%20societies%20is%20the%20Link%20Valley%20Resident%20Association%20in%20Kochi.%20Home%20to%20at%20least%20400%20people%2C%20the%20housing%20society%20now%20converts%20close%20to%20100%20kg%20of%20biodegradable%20waste%20into%20compost%2C%20thanks%20to%20Kenterra.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIts%20resident%20Binod%20Hariharan%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CSince%202008%2C%20we%20had%20a%20composting%20system%20for%20biodegradable%20waste.%20But%20we%20had%20to%20burn%20sanitary%20waste%20in%20our%20incinerators.%20Kenterra%20not%20only%20helped%20us%20in%20forward%20linking%20the%20manure%20that%20is%20generated%20but%20also%20in%20disposing%20of%20sanitary%20waste%20and%20biomedical%20waste%20in%20dedicated%20facilities.%20It%20is%20a%20big%20relief%20for%20us%20as%20all%20that%20waste%20is%20collected%20at%20our%20doorsteps%20on%20a%20daily%20basis%2C%20and%20we%20do%20not%20need%20to%20worry%20about%20its%20safe%20disposal.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDr%20Manoj%20informs%20that%20they%20are%20able%20to%20manage%20about%2010%2C000%20kg%20of%20waste%20every%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20Kerala%2C%2090%20percent%20of%20people%20today%20are%20segregating%20waste%20even%20at%20%3Cem%3Epanchayat%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20corporate%20levels.%20We%20do%20not%20have%20a%20single%20dumpsite%20in%20the%20state.%20When%20I%20step%20out%20of%20Kerala%2C%20I%20see%20how%20people%20unscientifically%20dispose%20of%20waste.%20I%20am%20glad%20I%20have%20been%20part%20of%20this%20change%20in%20my%20home%20state.%20I%20wish%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country%20follows%20to%20tackle%20this%20growing%20problem%20together%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Manoj%2C%20who%20was%20on%20his%20way%20to%20Delhi%20to%20discuss%20the%20implementation%20of%20this%20technology%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Kenterra%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697723717000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D332607%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Upset%20by%20the%20uncontrolled%20waste%20from%20apartments%20heading%20to%20landfills%2C%20Dr%20CN%20Manoj%2C%20a%20pharmaceutical%20scientist%2C%20founded%20'Kenterra'%20to%20handle%20all%20types%20of%20waste%20in%20Kerala%20and%20Bengaluru.%20He%20also%20created%20'Composorb%2C'%20a%20natural%20composting%20substance%20that%20transforms%20biodegradable%20waste%20into%20nourishing%20organic%20compost.%20Here's%20how%20they%20work.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332607%2Fkerala-pharma-scientist-kenterra-low-cost-solution-waste-management-compost-apartment-complex%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Love%20%E2%80%98Kulhad%20Chai%E2%80%99%3F%20Engineer-Turned-Entrepreneur%20Earns%20Crores%20Selling%20Traditional%20Clay%20Cups%22%2C%22content%22%3A