%2Fkulhad-1-1697721886.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fkulhad-1-1697721886-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fkulhad-1-1697721886-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fkulhad-1-1697721886-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fkulhad-1-1697721886-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-332626%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWith%20his%20kulhad%20business%2C%20Shobhit%20makes%20a%20whopping%20turnover%20of%20Rs%202.76%20crore%20per%20year.%C2%A0Picture%20credit%3A%20Shobhit%20Soni%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNo%20other%20cup%20%E2%80%94%20be%20it%20paper%20or%20glass%20%E2%80%94%20is%20as%20sustainable%20and%20eco-friendly%20as%20a%20clay%20cup.%20Even%20when%20we%20started%20our%20chai%20business%2C%20I%20was%20sure%20that%20I%20wanted%20to%20use%20%3Cem%3Ekulhads%20%3C%2Fem%3Eto%20serve%20the%20tea.%20With%20a%20network%20of%20%3Cem%3Ekulhad%20%3C%2Fem%3Emakers%20in%20various%20parts%20of%20the%20country%2C%20businesspersons%20will%20have%20an%20alternative%20to%20run%20their%20business%20eco-consciously%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFound%20Shobhit%E2%80%99s%20business%20idea%20interesting%3F%20You%20can%20reach%20him%20at%207300005969%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande)%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697723243000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D332610%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ajmer-resident%20Shobhit%20Soni%20always%20wanted%20to%20start%20his%20own%20company%20which%20would%20be%20both%20sustainable%2C%20and%20profit-making.%20He%20founded%20Mittisa%2C%20a%20brand%20that%20makes%20traditional%20kulhads%20(c